#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Registering with a Bootstrap Script (Salt and Traditional)"
msgstr "Registre amb un script Bootstrap (Sal i Tradicional)"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:2
msgid ""
"You can register Salt or traditional clients through the {productname} Proxy "
"with a bootstrap script.  This is done almost the same way as registering "
"clients directly with the {productname} Server.  The difference is that you "
"create the bootstrap script on the {productname} Proxy with a command line "
"tool.  The bootstrap script then deploys all necessary information to the "
"clients.  The bootstrap script requires some parameters such as activation "
"keys or GPG keys.  These parameters depend on your specific setup."
msgstr ""
"Podeu registrar Salt o clients tradicionals a través del servidor "
"intermediari {productname} amb un script bootstrap.  Això es fa gairebé de "
"la mateixa manera que registrar clients directament amb el servidor "
"{productname}.  La diferència és que creeu l'script bootstrap al servidor "
"intermediari {productname} amb una eina de línia d'ordres.  L'script "
"bootstrap desplega tota la informació necessària als clients.  L'script "
"bootstrap requereix alguns paràmetres com les claus d'activació o les claus "
"GPG.  Aquests paràmetres depenen de la configuració específica."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:3
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Registering Clients to a Proxy with a Bootstrap Script"
msgstr ""
"Procediment: Registre de clients a un servidor intermediari amb un script "
"Bootstrap"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:4
msgid ""
"Create a client activation key on the {productname} server using the "
"{webui}."
msgstr ""
"Creeu una clau d'activació del client al servidor {productname} utilitzant "
"la {webui}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:5
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-lifecycle.adoc:17
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:17
msgid "For more information, see xref:client-configuration:activation-keys.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per a més informació, vegeu xref:client-configuration:activation-keys.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:6
msgid ""
"On the proxy, execute the [command]``mgr-bootstrap`` command line tool as "
"{rootuser}."
msgstr ""
"Al servidor intermediari, executeu l'eina de línia d'ordres [command]}.mgr-"
"bootstrap}. com a {rootuser}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:7
msgid ""
"If needed, use the additional command line switches to tune your bootstrap "
"script.  To install a traditional client instead of a Salt client, ensure "
"you use the [command]``--traditional`` switch."
msgstr ""
"Si cal, utilitzeu els commutadors de línia d'ordres addicionals per afinar "
"l'script bootstrap.  Per instal·lar un client tradicional en comptes d'un "
"client Salt, assegureu-vos d'utilitzar el commutador [command].--"
"traditional.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:8
msgid ""
"To view available options type [command]``mgr-bootstrap --help`` from the "
"command line:"
msgstr ""
"Per veure les opcions disponibles escriviu [command] themgr-bootstrap --help "
"the des de la línia d'ordres:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-bootstrap --activation-keys=key-string\n"
msgstr "mgr-bootstrap --activation-keys=key-string\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:10
msgid "OPTIONAL: Edit the resulting bootstrap script."
msgstr "OPCIONAL: Edita l'script d'arrencada resultant."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:11
msgid ""
"Execute the bootstrap script directly on the clients or from the proxy with "
"[command]``ssh``.  Replace [systemitem]``<bootstrap>`` with the name of the "
"bootstrap script and [systemitem]`` <client.example.com>`` with the host "
"name of your client:"
msgstr ""
"Executa l'script bootstrap directament als clients o des del servidor "
"intermediari amb [command].ssh..  Reemplaça [systemitem] {<bootstrap> the "
"amb el nom de l'script bootstrap i [systemitem] { <client.example.com> the "
"amb el nom de l'amfitrió del vostre client:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-script.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "cat <bootstrap> | ssh root@<client.example.com> /bin/bash\n"
msgstr "cat <bootstrap>   arrel ssh root<client.example.com> /bin/bash\n"

#.  For more info, see client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc
#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Register Clients to a Proxy with the {webui}"
msgstr "Registra clients a un servidor intermediari amb {webui}"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:2
msgid "You can register Salt clients to the {productname} Proxy using the {webui}."
msgstr ""
"Podeu registrar clients de Salt al servidor intermediari {productname} "
"utilitzant la {webui}."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:3
msgid ""
"A bootstrap repository is needed for non-SLE clients in general and for SLE "
"clients before version 15.  A bootstrap repository offers packages for "
"installing Salt on clients and for registering Salt or traditional clients.  "
"For information about creating a bootstrap repository, see "
"xref:client-configuration:bootstrap-repository.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Es necessita un repositori d'arrencada per a clients no-SLE en general i per "
"a clients SLE abans de la versió 15.  Un repositori bootstrap ofereix "
"paquets per instal·lar Salt als clients i per registrar Salt o clients "
"tradicionals.  Per obtenir informació sobre la creació d'un repositori "
"bootstrap, vegeu xref:client-configuration:bootstrap-repository.adoc[]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:4
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Registering Clients to a Proxy with the {webui}"
msgstr "Procediment: Registre de clients a un servidor intermediari amb {webui}"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:5
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:7
msgid "In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[Bootstrapping]."
msgstr "A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Bootstrapping]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:6
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:8
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Host`` field, type the fully qualified domain name (FQDN) "
"of the client to be bootstrapped."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Host., escriviu el nom de domini (FQDN) completament "
"qualificat del client a arrencar."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:7
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:9
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``SSH Port`` field, type the SSH port number to use to "
"connect and bootstrap the client."
msgstr ""
"En el camp [guimenu].Port SSH., escriviu el número de port SSH a usar per a "
"connectar i arrencar el client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:8
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:10
msgid "By default, the SSH port is [systemitem]``22``."
msgstr "Per defecte, el port SSH és [systemitem].22.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:9
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:11
msgid "In the [guimenu]``User`` field, type the username to log in to the client."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Usuari., escriviu el nom d'usuari per a iniciar sessió amb "
"el client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:10
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:12
msgid "By default, the username is [systemitem]``root``."
msgstr "Per defecte, el nom d'usuari és [systemitem].root.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:11
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Authentication Method`` field, select the authentication "
"method to use for bootstrapping the client."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Mètode d'autenticació., seleccioneu el mètode "
"d'autenticació a utilitzar per arrencar el client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:12
msgid ""
"For password authentication, in the [guimenu]``Password`` field, type "
"password to log in to the client."
msgstr ""
"Per a l'autenticació de contrasenya, al camp [guimenu].Contrasenya., "
"escriviu la contrasenya per a iniciar sessió amb el client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:13
msgid ""
"For SSH Private key authentication, enter the private key and the associated "
"passphrase."
msgstr ""
"Per a l'autenticació de la clau privada SSH, introduïu la clau privada i la "
"contrasenya associada."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:14
msgid ""
"The key is only stored for as long as the bootstrapping process takes to "
"complete."
msgstr ""
"La clau només s'emmagatzemarà durant el temps que el procés d'arrencada es "
"requereixi per completar-se."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:15
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:16
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Activation Key`` field, select the activation key that is "
"associated with the software channel you want to use to bootstrap the "
"client."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Clau d'activitat., seleccioneu la clau d'activació "
"associada al canal de programari que voleu utilitzar per arrencar el client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:16
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Proxy`` field, select the proxy server you want to "
"register to."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Proxy., seleccioneu el servidor intermediari al qual voleu "
"registrar-vos."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:17
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:19
msgid ""
"By default, the [guimenu]``Disable SSH Strict Key Host Checking`` checkbox "
"is selected."
msgstr ""
"De manera predeterminada, està seleccionada la casella [guimenu].Desactiva "
"la comprovació de l'amfitrió de claus estrictes SSH``."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:18
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:20
msgid ""
"This allows the bootstrap process to automatically accept SSH host keys "
"without requiring you to manually authenticate."
msgstr ""
"Això permet que el procés bootstrap accepti automàticament les claus de "
"l'amfitrió SSH sense requerir que us autentiqueu manualment."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:19
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:21
msgid "OPTIONAL: Check the [guimenu]``Manage System Completely via SSH`` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"OPCIONAL: Marqueu la casella de selecció [guimenu].Gestioneu el sistema "
"completament mitjançant SSH.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:20
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:22
msgid ""
"If you check this option, the client is configured to use SSH for its "
"connection to the server, and no other connection method is configured."
msgstr ""
"Si marqueu aquesta opció, el client està configurat per utilitzar SSH per a "
"la seva connexió al servidor, i no hi ha cap altre mètode de connexió "
"configurat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:21
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:15
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:23
msgid "Click btn:[Bootstrap] to begin registration."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Bootstrap] per començar el registre."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-webui.adoc:22
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-webui.adoc:24
msgid ""
"When the bootstrap process has completed, your client is listed at "
"menu:Systems[System List]."
msgstr ""
"Quan el procés d'arrencada s'ha completat, el vostre client es llista al "
"menú:Systems[Llista de sistema]."

