#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Moving Salt or  Salt SSH Push Client between Proxies"
msgstr ""
"Procediment: Moure el client de Salt o Salt SSH Push entre servidors "
"intermediaris"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:10
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to the [guimenu]``System Details`` "
"page for the client you want to move between proxies."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu a la pàgina [guimenu].Detalls del sistema. "
"per al client que voleu moure entre servidors intermediaris."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:11
msgid ""
"Navigate to the [guimenu]``Connection`` tab.  Then follow the "
"[guimenu]``Change proxy`` link to see the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Navega a la pestanya [guimenu].Connection..  A continuació, seguiu l'enllaç "
"[guimenu].Canvia el servidor intermediari. per a veure el menú desplegable."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:12
msgid ""
"From the [guimenu]``New Proxy`` drop-down menu select the proxy you want the "
"client to move to, and click btn:[Change Proxy]."
msgstr ""
"Des del menú desplegable [guimenu]].Servei intermediari nou]. seleccioneu el "
"servidor intermediari al qual voleu que es mogui el client i feu clic a btn:["
"Canvia el servidor intermediari]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Procedure: Moving Multiple Salt or Salt SSH Push Clients between Proxies "
"with SSM"
msgstr ""
"Procediment: Moure múltiples clients de Salt o Salt SSH Push entre servidors "
"intermediaris amb SSM"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:14
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[System List] and "
"check each client to move, this adds the clients to the system set manager."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Llista de sistemes] i "
"comproveu cada client per moure, això afegeix els clients al gestor de "
"conjunts del sistema."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:15
msgid ""
"Navigate to menu:Systems[System Set Manager], and go to the "
"menu:Misc[Proxy]`` tab."
msgstr ""
"Navega al menú:Sistemes[Gestor de conjunts del sistema], i ves a la pestanya "
"menu:Misc[Proxy].."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:16
msgid ""
"From the [guimenu]``New Proxy`` drop-down menu select the proxy you want the "
"clients to move to, and click btn:[Change Proxy]."
msgstr ""
"Des del menú desplegable [guimenu]].Servidor intermediari nou]. seleccioneu "
"el servidor intermediari al qual voleu que es moguin els clients i feu clic "
"a btn:[Canvia el servidor intermediari]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:17
msgid ""
"The same functionality is also available with the "
"[systemitem]``system.changeProxy`` API call."
msgstr ""
"La mateixa funcionalitat també està disponible amb la crida de l'API "
"[systemitem].system.changeProxy.."

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Background Information"
msgstr "Informació de fons"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:19
msgid ""
"The effect of this function differs between normal Salt clients and Salt SSH "
"push clients."
msgstr ""
"L'efecte d'aquesta funció difereix entre clients de Salt normals i clients "
"de Salt SSH push."

#. type: Title ====
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "Normal Salt Clients"
msgstr "Clients normals de sal"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:21
msgid ""
"The function schedules a Salt state action, which modifies "
"[literal]``master:`` setting in the [path]``susemanager.conf`` Salt client "
"configuration file to point to the new proxy.  Then the function restarts "
"the Salt client."
msgstr ""
"La funció programa una acció d'estat de Salt, la qual modifica l'opció "
"[literal].master:. al fitxer de configuració del client [path]."
"susemanager.conf. Salt per a apuntar al nou servidor intermediari.  Després "
"la funció reinicia el client Salt."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:22
msgid ""
"Changing [literal]``master:`` by manually editing the "
"[path]``susemanager.conf`` file has the same effect and is supported, too."
msgstr ""
"Canviar [literal].master:. editant manualment el fitxer [path]."
"susemanager.conf. té el mateix efecte i també és compatible."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:23
msgid ""
"When the minion restarts and reconnects via the new proxy, the server "
"updates the proxy path in the database and schedules another action for "
"refreshing the channel URLs."
msgstr ""
"Quan el minion es reinicia i es torna a connectar a través del nou servidor "
"intermediari, el servidor actualitza el camí del servidor intermediari a la "
"base de dades i programa una altra acció per a actualitzar els URL del canal."

#. type: Title ====
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "Salt SSH Push Clients"
msgstr "Clients Salt SSH Push"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:25
msgid ""
"The function updates the proxy path immediately in the database and new "
"action for refreshing the channel URLs is scheduled."
msgstr ""
"La funció actualitza el camí del servidor intermediari immediatament a la "
"base de dades i es programa una nova acció per a actualitzar els URL del "
"canal."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Move Clients from Proxies to the Server"
msgstr "Mou els clients dels servidors intermediaris al servidor"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:27
msgid ""
"If you want to move a Salt client from a proxy to the server, select "
"[literal]``None`` from proxy list."
msgstr ""
"Si voleu moure un client Salt d'un servidor intermediari al servidor, "
"seleccioneu [literal].Cap from de la llista de servidors intermediaris."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy.adoc:28
msgid ""
"If you want to move a traditional client to the server you must repeat the "
"registration process from the beginning."
msgstr ""
"Si vols traslladar un client tradicional al servidor has de repetir el "
"procés de registre des del principi."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-lifecycle.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Upgrade Using the Content Lifecycle Manager"
msgstr "Actualitza usant el gestor de cicle de vida de contingut"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-lifecycle.adoc:2
msgid ""
"When you have many {sles} clients to manage, you can automate in-place "
"upgrades using the content lifecycle manager."
msgstr ""
"Quan teniu molts {sles} clients per gestionar, podeu automatitzar "
"actualitzacions in-place utilitzant el gestor de cicle de vida de contingut."

