#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Registering {rhel} Clients with RHUI"
msgstr "S'estan registrant {rhel} clients amb RHUI"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you are running {rhel} clients directly, rather than using {sleses}, you "
"need to use Red Hat sources to retrieve and update packages.  This section "
"contains information about using {redhat} update infrastructure (RHUI) to "
"register traditional and Salt clients running {rhel} operating systems.  If "
"you are running your clients in a public cloud, such as Amazon EC2, use this "
"method."
msgstr ""
"Si esteu executant directament {rhel} clients, en lloc d'utilitzar {sleses}, "
"heu d'utilitzar fonts de Red Hat per recuperar i actualitzar paquets.  "
"Aquesta secció conté informació sobre l'ús de la infraestructura "
"d'actualització {redhat} (RHUI) per registrar clients tradicionals i de Salt "
"que executen sistemes operatius {rhel}.  Si estàs executant els teus clients "
"en un núvol públic, com Amazon EC2, utilitza aquest mètode."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:3
msgid ""
"It is possible to use RHUI in conjunction with the {redhat} content delivery "
"network (CDN) to manage your {rhel} subscriptions.  For information about "
"using {redhat} CDN, see xref:client-configuration:clients-rh-cdn.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"És possible utilitzar RHUI juntament amb la xarxa de distribució de "
"continguts {redhat} (CDN) per gestionar les vostres subscripcions {rhel}.  "
"Per obtenir informació sobre l'ús del CDN {redhat}, vegeu xref:client-"
"configuration:clients-rh-cdn.adoc[]."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:4
msgid ""
"{rhel} clients are based on {redhat} and are unrelated to {sleses}, RES, or "
"{sles}.  You are responsible for connecting {productname} Server to the "
"{redhat} update infrastructure.  All clients that get updates using this "
"RHUI certificate need to be correctly licensed, please check with your cloud "
"provider and the {redhat} terms of service for more information."
msgstr ""
"Els clients de {rhel} es basen en {redhat} i no estan relacionats amb "
"{sleses}, RES o {sles}.  Sou responsable de connectar {productname} Servidor "
"a la infraestructura d'actualització {redhat}.  Tots els clients que obtenen "
"actualitzacions utilitzant aquest certificat RHUI han de tenir una llicència "
"correcta, si us plau, comproveu amb el vostre proveïdor de núvols i les "
"condicions del servei {redhat} per a més informació."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:5
msgid ""
"When {rhel} clients registered with RHUI are switched off, {redhat} might "
"declare the certificate invalid.  In this case, you need to turn the client "
"on again, or get a new RHUI certificate."
msgstr ""
"Quan {rhel} clients registrats amb RHUI estan desactivats, {redhat} podria "
"declarar que el certificat no és vàlid.  En aquest cas, cal activar de nou "
"el client, o obtenir un nou certificat RHUI."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:14
msgid ""
"This guide covers clients registered to {redhat} update infrastructure "
"(RHUI).  You must have at least one system registered to RHUI, with an "
"authorized subscription for repository content."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta guia cobreix els clients registrats a la infraestructura "
"d'actualització {redhat} (RHUI).  Heu de tenir almenys un sistema registrat "
"a RHUI, amb una subscripció autoritzada per al contingut del repositori."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:15
msgid ""
"For information about using {redhat} content delivery network (CDN) instead, "
"see xref:client-configuration:clients-rh-cdn.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per obtenir informació sobre com utilitzar {redhat} xarxa de lliurament de "
"contingut (CDN), vegeu xref:client-configuration:clients-rh-cdn.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:17
msgid ""
"The entitlement certificates and keys need to be copied from the client "
"system to a location that the {productname} Server can access."
msgstr ""
"Els certificats i claus de drets s'han de copiar del sistema client a una "
"ubicació a la qual el servidor {productname} pugui accedir."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:18
msgid ""
"The keys and certificates might have slightly different names to those shown "
"here.  Your entitlement certificate and the {redhat} CA Certificate file "
"have file extensions of [path]``.crt``.  The key has a file extension of "
"[path]``.key``."
msgstr ""
"Les claus i els certificats poden tenir noms lleugerament diferents dels que "
"es mostren aquí.  El vostre certificat de títol i el fitxer de certificat CA "
"{redhat} tenen extensions de fitxer de [camí]..crt..  La clau té una "
"extensió de fitxer de [path]..key.."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Copying Certificates to the Server"
msgstr "Procediment: Còpia de certificats al servidor"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:20
msgid ""
"Copy your entitlement certificate and key from the client system, to a "
"location that the {productname} Server can access. Amazon EC2:"
msgstr ""
"Copieu el vostre certificat de dret i la clau del sistema client, a una "
"ubicació a la qual el servidor {productname} pot accedir. Amazon EC2:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/product/content-<version>.crt /<example>/entitlement/\n"
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/content-<version>.key /<example>/entitlement/\n"
msgstr ""
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/product/content-<version>.crt /<example>/entitlement/\n"
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/content-<version>.key /<example>/entitlement/\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:22
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:27
msgid "Google Cloud Platform:"
msgstr "Plataforma Google Cloud:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/product/content.crt /<example>/entitlement/\n"
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/key.pem /<example>/entitlement/\n"
msgstr ""
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/product/content.crt /<example>/entitlement/\n"
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/key.pem /<example>/entitlement/\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:24
msgid ""
"Copy the {redhat} CA Certificate file from the client system, to the same "
"location as the entitlement certificate and key:"
msgstr ""
"Copieu el fitxer de certificat CA {redhat} del sistema client, a la mateixa "
"ubicació que el certificat i la clau de títol:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "cp /etc/pki/rhui/cdn.redhat.com-chain.crt /<example>/entitlement\n"
msgstr "cp /etc/pki/rhui/cdn.redhat.com-chain.crt /<example>/entitlement\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "cp /etc/pki/rhui/ca.crt /<example>/entitlement\n"
msgstr "cp /etc/pki/rhui/ca.crt /<example>/entitlement\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:33
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Description`` field, type "
"[systemitem]``Entitlement-Cert-Date``."
msgstr "Al camp [guimenu].Descripció., escriviu [systemitem].títol-Cert-Date.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:35
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Select file to upload`` field, browse to the location "
"where you saved the entitlement certificate, and select the [path]``.crt`` "
"certificate file."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Seleccioneu fitxer per a pujar., navegueu fins a la "
"ubicació on heu desat el certificat de títol i seleccioneu el fitxer de "
"certificat [path]..crt.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:38
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Description`` field, type "
"[systemitem]``Entitlement-Key-Date``."
msgstr "Al camp [guimenu].Descripció., escriviu [systemitem].títol-Clau-Data.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:40
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Select file to upload`` field, browse to the location "
"where you saved the entitlement key, and select the [path]``.key`` key file."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Seleccioneu fitxer per a pujar., navegueu fins a la "
"ubicació on heu desat la clau de títol i seleccioneu el fitxer de clau "
"[camí]..key.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:43
msgid "In the [guimenu]``Description`` field, type [systemitem]``redhat-cert``."
msgstr "Al camp [guimenu].Descripció., escriviu [systemitem].redhat-cert.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:48
msgid ""
"To mirror the software from RHUI, you need to create custom channels and "
"repositories in {productname} that are linked to RHUI by a URL.  You must "
"have entitlements to these products in your Red Hat Portal for this to work "
"correctly.  You can use the yum utility to get the URLs of the repositories "
"you want to mirror:"
msgstr ""
"Per a reflectir el programari de RHUI, heu de crear canals i repositoris "
"personalitzats a {productname} que estan enllaçats a RHUI per un URL.  Has "
"de tenir dret a aquests productes al teu Red Hat Portal perquè això funcioni "
"correctament.  Podeu utilitzar la utilitat yum per a obtenir els URL dels "
"repositoris que voleu reflectir:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "yum repolist -v | grep baseurl\n"
msgstr "yum repolist -v   grep baseurl\n"

