#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:72
msgid ""
"To use RHUI, you need to manually add the required HTTP headers to the "
"configuration file.  Without them, you cannot successfully perform a client "
"synchronization."
msgstr ""
"Per utilitzar RHUI, heu d'afegir manualment les capçaleres HTTP necessàries "
"al fitxer de configuració.  Sense ells, no es pot realitzar correctament una "
"sincronització de client."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:73
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Adding HTTP Headers to the Configuration File"
msgstr "Procediment: Afegir capçaleres HTTP al fitxer de configuració"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:74
msgid ""
"Locate the [systemitem]``X-RHUI-ID`` and [systemitem]``X-RHUI-SIGNATURE`` "
"HTTP headers from your RHUI instance."
msgstr ""
"Localitzeu les capçaleres HTTP [systemitem].X-RHUI-ID. i [systemitem].X-RHUI-"
"SIGNATURE. des de la vostra instància RHUI."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:75
msgid ""
"You can use these commands on the {redhat} client to get the values from the "
"cloud instance metadata API at [systemitem]``169.254.169.254``:"
msgstr ""
"Podeu utilitzar aquestes ordres al client {redhat} per obtenir els valors de "
"l'API de metadades de la instància del núvol a [systemitem] at169.254.169."
"254::"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:76
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"echo \"X-RHUI-ID=$(curl -s "
"http://169.254.169.254/latest/dynamic/instance-identity/document|base64|tr "
"-d '\\n')\"\n"
"echo \"X-RHUI-SIGNATURE=$(curl -s "
"http://169.254.169.254/latest/dynamic/instance-identity/signature|base64|tr "
"-d '\\n')\"\n"
msgstr ""
"echo \"X-RHUI-ID$$(curl -s http://169.254.169.254/latest/dynamic/"
"instance-identity/document\"base64\"tr -d '\\n"
"')\" echo \"X-RHUI-SIGNATURE\"$(curl -s http://169.254.169.254/latest/"
"dynamic/instance-identity/signature\"base64\"tr -d '\\n"
"')\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:77
msgid ""
"Open the [path]``/etc/rhn/spacewalk-repo-sync/extra_headers.conf`` "
"configuration file, and add or edit these lines with the correct "
"information:"
msgstr ""
"Obriu el fitxer de configuració [path] the/etc/rhn/spacewalk-repo-sync/"
"extraheaders.conf, i afegiu o editeu aquestes línies amb la informació "
"correcta:"

