#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "SUSE Manager Daemon (rhnsd)"
msgstr "Dimoni del gestor SUSE (rhnsd)"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:3
msgid ""
"It is only used on {sle}{nbsp}11 and {rhnminrelease6}, as these systems do "
"not use systemd.  On later operating systems, a systemd timer "
"([systemitem]``rhnsd.timer``) is used and controlled by "
"[systemitem]``rhnsd.service``."
msgstr ""
"Només s'utilitza a {sle}{nbsp}11 i {rhnminrelease6}, ja que aquests sistemes "
"no utilitzen systemd.  En sistemes operatius posteriors, un temporitzador "
"systemd ([systemitem].rhnsd.timer.) és utilitzat i controlat per [systemitem]"
".rhnsd.service.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:4
msgid "Start the daemon with [command]``/etc/init.d/rhnsd``."
msgstr "Inicia el dimoni amb [command]./etc/init.d/rhnsd.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:5
msgid ""
"By default, it checks every four hours for new actions.  This means it can "
"take some time for clients to execute scheduled actions."
msgstr ""
"Per defecte, comprova cada quatre hores si hi ha accions noves.  Això vol "
"dir que pot trigar una mica a executar les accions programades."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:6
msgid ""
"To check for updates, [systemitem]``rhnsd`` runs the external "
"[systemitem]``mgr_check`` program located in [path]``/usr/sbin/``.  This is "
"a small application that establishes the network connection to "
"{productname}.  The {productname} daemon does not listen on any network "
"ports or talk to the network directly.  All network activity is performed by "
"the [systemitem]``mgr_check`` utility."
msgstr ""
"Per a comprovar si hi ha actualitzacions, [systemitem].rhnsd. executa el "
"programa extern [systemitem].mgrcheck. situat a [path]./usr/sbin/..  Aquesta "
"és una aplicació petita que estableix la connexió de xarxa a {productname}.  "
"El dimoni {productname} no escolta cap port de xarxa ni parla directament "
"amb la xarxa.  Tota l'activitat de la xarxa la realitza la utilitat "
"[systemitem].mgrcheck.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:7
msgid ""
"This figure provides an overview of the default [systemitem]``rhnsd`` "
"process path.  All items left of the [systemitem]``Python XMLRPC server`` "
"block represent processes running on the {productname} client."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta figura proporciona una visió general del camí predeterminat del "
"procés [systemitem].rhnsd..  Tots els elements que queden del bloc "
"[systemitem].Servidor XMLRPC de Python. representen processos que s'executen "
"al client {productname}."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "rhnsd-taigon.png"
msgstr "rhnsd-taigon.png"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configure rhnsd"
msgstr "Configurar rhnsd"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:10
msgid ""
"The `rhnsd` initialization script has a configuration file on the client "
"system at [path]``/etc/sysconfig/rhn/rhnsd``."
msgstr ""
"L'script d'inicialització .rhnsd. té un fitxer de configuració al sistema "
"client a [path]./etc/sysconfig/rhn/rhnsd.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:11
msgid ""
"An important parameter for the daemon is its check-in frequency.  The "
"default interval time is four hours (240 minutes).  The minimum allowed time "
"interval is one hour (60 minutes).  If you set the interval below one hour, "
"it changes back to the default of 4 hours (240 minutes)."
msgstr ""
"Un paràmetre important per al dimoni és la seva freqüència de facturació.  "
"El temps d'interval per defecte és de quatre hores (240 minuts).  L'interval "
"de temps mínim permès és d'una hora (60 minuts).  Si establiu l'interval per "
"sota d'una hora, es tornarà a canviar al valor per defecte de 4 hores (240 "
"minuts)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:12
msgid ""
"If you modify the `rhnsd` configuration file, execute this command as root "
"to restart the daemon and pick up your changes:"
msgstr ""
"Si modifiqueu el fitxer de configuració  therhnsd,, executeu aquesta ordre "
"com a root per a reiniciar el dimoni i recollir els canvis:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/init.d/rhnsd restart\n"
msgstr "/etc/init.d/rhnsd reinicia\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:14
msgid "To see the status of `rhnsd`, use this command as root:"
msgstr "Per a veure l'estat de  therhnsd,, utilitzeu aquesta ordre com a root:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/init.d/rhnsd status\n"
msgstr "/etc/init.d/rhnsd status\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:16
msgid ""
"On {sle}{nbsp}12 and later, the default time interval is set in "
"[path]``/etc/systemd/system/timers.target.wants/rhnsd.timer``, in this "
"section:"
msgstr ""
"A {sle}{nbsp}12 i posteriors, l'interval de temps predeterminat s'estableix "
"a [path] in/etc/systemd/system/timers.target.wants/rhnsd.timer in, en "
"aquesta secció:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[Timer]\n"
"OnCalendar=00/4:00\n"
"RandomizedDelaySec=30min\n"
msgstr ""
"[Temporitzador]\n"
"OnCalendar0000/4:00\n"
"RandomizedDelaySec3030min\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:18
msgid ""
"You can create an overriding drop-in file for [path]``rhnsd.timer`` using "
"[command]``systemctl``:"
msgstr ""
"Podeu crear un fitxer desplegable anul·lant per a [path]:rhnsd.timer: "
"utilitzant [command]:systemctl::"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "systemctl edit rhnsd.timer\n"
msgstr "systemctl edit rhnsd.timer\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:20
msgid "For example, if you want configure a two hour time interval:"
msgstr "Per exemple, si voleu configurar un interval de temps de dues hores:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[Timer]\n"
"OnCalendar=00/2:00\n"
msgstr ""
"[Temporitzador]\n"
"OnCalendar0000/2:00\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:22
msgid ""
"The file is saved as "
"[path]``/etc/systemd/system/rhnsd.timer.d/override.conf``."
msgstr ""
"El fitxer es desa com a [camí]./etc/systemd/system/rhnsd.timer.d/override."
"conf.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-rhnsd.adoc:23
msgid ""
"For more information about systemd timers, see the "
"[command]``systemd.timer`` and [command]``systemctl`` manpages."
msgstr ""
"Per a més informació sobre els temporitzadors systemd, vegeu les pàgines man "
"[command].systemd.timer. i [command].systemctl.."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-salt.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Contact Methods for Salt Clients"
msgstr "Mètodes de contacte per a clients de Salt"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-salt.adoc:2
msgid ""
"In most cases, Salt clients are registered accurately with the default "
"bootstrap methods."
msgstr ""
"En la majoria dels casos, els clients de Salt es registren amb precisió amb "
"els mètodes d'arrencada per defecte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-salt.adoc:3
msgid ""
"If you need to use Salt clients in a disconnected setup, you can configure "
"Push via Salt SSH.  In this environment, clients are located in a "
"firewall-protected zone called DMZ.  For more information about Salt SSH "
"contact method, see "
"xref:client-configuration:contact-methods-saltssh.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Si heu d'utilitzar clients de Salt en una configuració desconnectada, podeu "
"configurar Push mitjançant Salt SSH.  En aquest entorn, els clients es "
"troben en una zona protegida amb tallafoc anomenada DMZ.  Per obtenir més "
"informació sobre el mètode de contacte SSH de Salt, vegeu xref:client-"
"configuration:contact-methods-saltssh.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-salt.adoc:4
msgid ""
"If you need to manually configure a Salt client to connect to the "
"{productname} Server, edit the Salt client configuration file with the "
"correct network details.  For more information about Salt minion "
"configuration file contact method, see "
"xref:client-configuration:registration-cli.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Si necessiteu configurar manualment un client Salt per connectar-vos al "
"servidor {productname}, editeu el fitxer de configuració del client Salt amb "
"els detalls de la xarxa correctes.  Per obtenir més informació sobre el "
"mètode de contacte del fitxer de configuració de Salt minion, vegeu xref"
":client-configuration:registration-cli.adoc[]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-salt.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "Onboarding Details"
msgstr "Detalls de l'Onboarding"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-salt.adoc:6
msgid ""
"Salt has its own database to keep the keys for the minions. This needs to be "
"kept in sync with the {productname} database.  As soon as the key is "
"accepted in Salt, the onboarding process in {productname} starts.  The "
"onboarding process will look for existing systems in the {productname} "
"database by searching for the ``minion_id`` and the ``machine-id``.  If "
"nothing is found, the new system gets created.  In case an entry with the "
"``minion_id`` or the ``machine-id`` is found, that system will be migrated "
"to match the new system.  In case there is a match for both entries, and "
"they are not the same system, the onboarding will be aborted with an error.  "
"In this case the administrator needs to resolve the conflict by removing at "
"least on of the systems."
msgstr ""
"Salt disposa d'una base de dades pròpia per guardar les claus dels minions. "
"Això s'ha de mantenir sincronitzat amb la base de dades {productname}.  Tan "
"aviat com s'accepta la clau a Salt, s'inicia el procés d'onboarding a "
"{productname}.  El procés d'onboarding cercarà sistemes existents a la base "
"de dades {productname} cercant el .minionid. i el .machine-id..  Si no es "
"troba res, es crea el nou sistema.  En cas que es trobi una entrada amb el ."
"minionid. o el .machine-id., aquest sistema serà migrat per a coincidir amb "
"el nou sistema.  En cas que hi hagi una coincidència per a les dues "
"entrades, i no siguin el mateix sistema, l'onboarding s'interromprà amb un "
"error.  En aquest cas, l'administrador ha de resoldre el conflicte eliminant "
"almenys els sistemes."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Salt Bundle"
msgstr "Salt Bundle"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "What is Salt Bundle?"
msgstr "Què és Salt Bundle?"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:3
msgid ""
"The Salt Bundle is a single binary package containing Salt Minion, Python 3, "
"required Python modules, and libraries."
msgstr ""
"El Salt Bundle és un únic paquet binari que conté Salt Minion, Python 3, "
"mòduls de Python necessaris i biblioteques."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:4
msgid ""
"The Salt Bundle is shipped with Python 3 and all the requirements for Salt "
"to run. Thus Salt Bundle does not use the Python version install on the "
"client as system software.  The Salt Bundle can be installed on clients that "
"do not meet the requirements for a given Salt version."
msgstr ""
"El Salt Bundle s'envia amb Python 3 i tots els requisits perquè Salt "
"funcioni. Per tant, Salt Bundle no utilitza la versió Python d'instal·lació "
"al client com a programari del sistema.  El Salt Bundle es pot instal·lar en "
"clients que no compleixen els requisits per a una versió de Salt determinada."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:5
msgid ""
"It is also possible to use the Salt Bundle on systems that run a Salt Minion "
"connected to a Salt Master other than the {productname} Salt Master."
msgstr ""
"També és possible utilitzar el Salt Bundle en sistemes que executen un Salt "
"Minion connectat a un Salt Master diferent del Salt Master {productname}."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Client Registration with Salt Bundle as a Minion"
msgstr "Registre del client amb Salt Bundle com a Minion"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:7
msgid ""
"The registration method with the Salt Bundle is the recommended registration "
"method.  This section explains the advantages and limitations of the current "
"implementation.  The Salt Bundle is provided as the "
"[package]``venv-salt-minion`` that consists of Salt, Python 3, and the "
"Python modules Salt depends on.  Bootstrapping with {webui} is using Salt "
"Bundle as well, so bootstrapping with {webui} is not Python dependant.  "
"Using the Salt Bundle, it is no longer needed that the client provides any "
"Python interpreter or modules."
msgstr ""
"El mètode de registre amb el Salt Bundle és el mètode de registre "
"recomanat.  En aquest apartat s'expliquen els avantatges i limitacions de la "
"implementació actual.  El Salt Bundle es proporciona com el [package].venv-"
"salt-minion. que consisteix en Salt, Python 3, i els mòduls de Python Salt "
"en depenen.  L'arrencada amb {webui} també està utilitzant Salt Bundle, de "
"manera que l'arrencada amb {webui} no depèn de Python.  Utilitzant el Salt "
"Bundle, ja no és necessari que el client proporcioni cap intèrpret o mòdul "
"de Python."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:8
msgid ""
"If you bootstrap new clients, registration with the Salt Bundle is the "
"default method.  You can switch existing clients to the Salt Bundle method.  "
"If you switch, the [package]``salt-minion`` package and its dependencies "
"will stay installed."
msgstr ""
"Si arrenqueu clients nous, registrar-vos amb el Salt Bundle és el mètode per "
"defecte.  Podeu canviar els clients existents al mètode Salt Bundle.  Si "
"canvieu, el paquet [package].salt-minion. i les seves dependències romandran "
"instal·lades."

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using the Salt Bundle with the Salt Minion"
msgstr "Utilització del Salt Bundle amb el Salt Minion"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:10
msgid ""
"The Salt Bundle can be used with the Salt Minion managed by the Salt Master "
"other than {productname} Server at the same time.  If the Salt Bundle is "
"installed on a client {productname} Server will manage the configuration "
"files of the Salt Bundle, the configuration files of "
"[literal]``salt-minion`` will not be managed in this case.  For more "
"information, see "
"xref:client-configuration:registration-cli.adoc#_salt_bundle_configuration[Salt "
"Bundle configuration]."
msgstr ""
"El Salt Bundle es pot utilitzar amb el Salt Minion gestionat pel Salt Master "
"a part de {productname} Server al mateix temps.  Si el Salt Bundle està "
"instal·lat en un client {productname} Server gestionarà els fitxers de "
"configuració del Salt Bundle, en aquest cas no es gestionaran els fitxers de "
"configuració de [literal].salt-minion..  Per a més informació, vegeu xref"
":client-configuration:registration-cli.adoc].saltbundleconfiguration[Salt "
"Bundle configuration]."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:11
msgid ""
"To bootstrap a client with the Salt Minion managed by the Salt Master other "
"than {productname} Server it is recommended to use "
"[command]``mgr-bootstrap`` [option]``--force-bundle`` when generating the "
"bootstrap script, or to set [option]``FORCE_VENV_SALT_MINION`` to `1` in the "
"bootstrap script.  For bootstrapping with {webui} "
"[literal]``mgr_force_venv_salt_minion`` set to [literal]``true`` pillar can "
"be specified globally.  For more information, see "
"xref:specialized-guides:salt/salt-states-and-pillars.adoc[Salt States and "
"Pillars]."
msgstr ""
"Per arrencar un client amb el Salt Minion gestionat pel Salt Master a part "
"de {productname} Server es recomana utilitzar [command].mgr-bootstrap when "
"[option].--force-bundle. quan es genera l'script bootstrap, o establir "
"[option].FORCEVENVSALTMINION. a 11. en l'script bootstrap.  Per arrencar amb "
"{webui} [literal].mgrforcevenvsaltminion. establert a [literal].true. pilar "
"es pot especificar globalment.  Per a més informació, vegeu xref:specialized-"
"guides:salt/salt-states-and-pillars.adoc[Estats i pilars de sal]."

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Switching from Salt Minion to Salt Bundle"
msgstr "Canviar de minion de sal a Salt Bundle"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:13
msgid ""
"The Salt state [literal]``util.mgr_switch_to_venv_minion`` is available to "
"switch from [package]``salt-minion`` to [package]``venv-salt-minion``.  It "
"is recommended to switch to [package]``venv-salt-minion`` in two steps to "
"avoid trouble with shifting processes:"
msgstr ""
"L'estat de sal [literal].util.mgrswitchtovenvminion. està disponible per "
"canviar de [package].salt-minion to a [package].venv-salt-minion..  Es "
"recomana canviar a [package] invenv-salt-minion in en dos passos per evitar "
"problemes amb els processos de desplaçament:"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Procedure: Switching with [literal]``util.mgr_switch_to_venv_minion`` state "
"to [package]``venv-salt-minion``"
msgstr ""
"Procediment: Canvi amb [literal] toutil.mgrswitchtovenvminion to estat a "
"[package] tovenv-salt-minion to"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:15
msgid ""
"Apply [literal]``util.mgr_switch_to_venv_minion`` with no pillar specified "
"first.  This will result in the switch to [package]``venv-salt-minion`` with "
"copying configuration files etc.  It will not clean up the original "
"[package]``salt-minion`` configurations and its packages."
msgstr ""
"Aplica [literal].util.mgrswitchtovenvminion. sense cap pilar especificat "
"primer.  Això resultarà en el canvi a [package].venv-salt-minion. amb la "
"còpia de fitxers de configuració, etc. No netejarà les configuracions "
"originals [package].salt-minion. i els seus paquets."

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt <minion_id> state.apply util.mgr_switch_to_venv_minion\n"
msgstr "sal <minionid> estat.apply util.mgrswitchtovenvminion\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:17
msgid ""
"Apply [literal]``util.mgr_switch_to_venv_minion`` with "
"[literal]``mgr_purge_non_venv_salt`` set to [literal]``True`` to remove "
"[package]``salt-minion`` and with [literal]``mgr_purge_non_venv_salt_files`` "
"set to [literal]``True`` to remove all the files related to "
"[package]``salt-minion``.  This second step ensures the first step was "
"processed, and then removes the old configuration files and the now obsolete "
"[package]``salt-minion`` package."
msgstr ""
"Aplica [literal].util.mgrswitchtovenvminion. amb [literal]."
"mgrpurgenonvenvsalt. establert a [literal].True to per eliminar [package] "
"tosalt-minion to i amb [literal].mgrpurgenonvenvsaltfiles. establert a "
"[literal].True. per eliminar tots els fitxers relacionats amb [package].salt-"
"minion..  Aquest segon pas assegura que el primer pas s'ha processat, i "
"després elimina els fitxers de configuració antics i el paquet [package"
"].salt-minion. ara obsolet."

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"salt <minion_id> state.apply util.mgr_switch_to_venv_minion "
"pillar='{\"mgr_purge_non_venv_salt_files\": True, "
"\"mgr_purge_non_venv_salt\": True}'\n"
msgstr ""
"sal <minionid> estat.aplica util.mgrswitchtovenvminion pilar\":'{"
"\"mgrpurgenonvenvsaltfiles\": Cert, \"mgrpurgenonvenvsalt\": Cert}'\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:19
msgid ""
"In case of running the second step of switching with skipping the first "
"step, state apply process could fail as it requires stopping the "
"[systemitem]``salt-minion`` which is used to execute the command on the "
"client side."
msgstr ""
"En cas d'executar el segon pas de commutar amb saltar el primer pas, el "
"procés d'aplicació d'estat podria fallar, ja que requereix aturar el "
"[systemitem]altsalt-minion. que s'utilitza per executar l'ordre al costat "
"del client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:20
msgid ""
"On the other hand, it is also possible to avoid installing the Salt Bundle "
"and keep using [package]``salt-minion`` instead.  In this case, specify one "
"of these options:"
msgstr ""
"D'altra banda, també és possible evitar instal·lar el Salt Bundle i seguir "
"utilitzant [package].salt-minion. en el seu lloc.  En aquest cas, "
"especifiqueu una d'aquestes opcions:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:21
msgid "Execute [command]``mgr-bootstrap`` with [option]``--no-bundle`` option."
msgstr "Executa [command].mgr-bootstrap with amb l'opció [option].--no-bundle.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:22
msgid ""
"Set [literal]``AVOID_VENV_SALT_MINION`` to [literal]``1`` in the generated "
"bootstrap script."
msgstr ""
"Estableix [literal].AVOIDVENVSALTMINION to a [literal]11. a l'script "
"d'arrencada generat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:23
msgid ""
"For bootstrap state set the [literal]``mgr_avoid_venv_salt_minion`` pillar "
"to [literal]``True``."
msgstr ""
"Per a l'estat de bootstrap establiu el pilar [literal]."
"mgravoidvenvsaltminion. a [literal].True.."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "Salt SSH with the Salt Bundle"
msgstr "Salt SSH amb el Salt Bundle"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:25
msgid "The Salt Bundle is also used when performing Salt SSH actions to clients."
msgstr ""
"El Salt Bundle també s'utilitza quan es realitzen accions de Salt SSH als "
"clients."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:26
msgid ""
"A shell script deploys the Salt Bundle onto the target system without "
"installing [package]``venv-salt-minion`` before any Salt command is "
"executed. Since the Salt Bundle contains the whole Salt code base, no "
"[literal]``salt-thin`` is deployed. Salt SSH (including bootstrapping using "
"the {webui}) uses the Python 3 interpreter within the bundle. The target "
"system does not need to have any other Python interpreter installed."
msgstr ""
"Un script de shell desplega el Salt Bundle al sistema de destinació sense "
"instal·lar [package].venv-salt-minion before abans d'executar qualsevol "
"ordre Salt. Atès que el Salt Bundle conté tota la base del codi Salt, no es "
"desplega [literal]altsal-thin.. Salt SSH (inclosa l'arrencada mitjançant la "
"{webui}) utilitza l'intèrpret Python 3 dins del paquet. El sistema de "
"destinació no necessita tenir instal·lat cap altre intèrpret de Python."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:27
msgid ""
"The Python 3 deployed with the Bundle is used to handle Salt SSH session on "
"the client, so Salt SSH (including bootstrapping with {webui}) is not "
"dependant on Python installed on the system."
msgstr ""
"El Python 3 desplegat amb el Bundle s'utilitza per gestionar la sessió Salt "
"SSH al client, de manera que Salt SSH (inclosa l'arrencada amb {webui}) no "
"depèn de Python instal·lat al sistema."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:28
msgid ""
"The bootstrap repository must be created before bootstrapping the client "
"with {webui}. Salt SSH is using the Salt Bundle taken from the bootstrap "
"repository based on the detected target operating system.  For more "
"information, see "
"xref:client-configuration:bootstrap-repository.adoc#_prepare_to_create_a_bootstrap_repository[Prepare "
"to Create a Bootstrap Repository]"
msgstr ""
"Cal crear el repositori bootstrap abans d'arrencar el client amb {webui}. "
"Salt SSH està utilitzant el Salt Bundle agafat del repositori bootstrap "
"basat en el sistema operatiu de destinació detectat.  Per a més informació, "
"vegeu xref:client-configuration:bootstrap-repository."
"adoc]preparetocreateabootstraprepository[Prepare to Create a Bootstrap "
"Repository]"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc:29
msgid ""
"Using `salt-thin` can be enabled as a fallback method, but it requires "
"Python 3 to be installed on the client.  This method is not recommended nor "
"supported and exists for development purposes only.  Set "
"[option]``web.ssh_use_salt_thin`` to `true` in the "
"[path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` configuration file."
msgstr ""
"L'ús de «salt-thin» es pot activar com a mètode alternatiu, però requereix "
"que el Python 3 s'instal·li al client.  Aquest mètode no es recomana ni es "
"recolza i només existeix amb finalitats de desenvolupament.  Estableix "
"[option].web.sshusesaltthin to a .true in al fitxer de configuració [path]./"
"etc/rhn/rhn.conf.."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Push via Salt SSH"
msgstr "Empènyer a través de Salt SSH"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Push via Salt SSH is used in environments where Salt clients cannot reach "
"the {productname} Server directly.  In this environment, clients are located "
"in a firewall-protected zone called a DMZ.  No system within the DMZ is "
"authorized to open a connection to the internal network, including the "
"{productname} Server."
msgstr ""
"Push via Salt SSH s'utilitza en entorns on els clients de Salt no poden "
"arribar directament al servidor {productname}.  En aquest entorn, els "
"clients es troben en una zona protegida amb tallafoc anomenada DMZ.  Cap "
"sistema dins de la DMZ està autoritzat a obrir una connexió a la xarxa "
"interna, inclòs el servidor {productname}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:3
msgid ""
"The Push via Salt SSH method creates an encrypted tunnel from the "
"{productname} Server on the internal network to the clients located on the "
"DMZ.  After all actions and events are executed, the tunnel is closed."
msgstr ""
"El mètode Push via Salt SSH crea un túnel encriptat des del servidor "
"{productname} a la xarxa interna als clients ubicats a la DMZ.  Després "
"d'executar totes les accions i esdeveniments, el túnel es tanca."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:4
msgid ""
"The server uses the Salt SSH to contact the clients at regular intervals, "
"checking in and performing scheduled actions and events.  For more "
"information about Salt SSH, see "
"xref:specialized-guides:salt/salt-ssh.adoc[Salt SSH]."
msgstr ""
"El servidor utilitza el Salt SSH per contactar amb els clients a intervals "
"regulars, comprovant i realitzant accions i esdeveniments programats.  Per a "
"més informació sobre Salt SSH, vegeu xref:specialized-guides:salt/salt-ssh."
"adoc[Salt SSH]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:5
msgid ""
"This contact method works for Salt clients only.  For traditional clients, "
"use Push via SSH."
msgstr ""
"Aquest mètode de contacte només funciona per a clients de Salt.  Per als "
"clients tradicionals, utilitzeu Push a través de SSH."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:6
msgid ""
"This image demonstrates the Push via Salt SSH process path.  All items left "
"of the [systemitem]``Taskomatic`` block represent processes running on the "
"{productname} client."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta imatge mostra el camí del procés Push via Salt SSH.  Tots els "
"elements que queden del bloc [systemitem].Taskomatic. representen processos "
"que s'executen al client {productname}."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt-ssh-contact-taigon.png"
msgstr "salt-ssh-contact-taigon.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:8
msgid ""
"To use Push via Salt SSH, you must have the SSH daemon running on the "
"client, and reachable by the [systemitem]``salt-api`` daemon running on the "
"{productname} Server.  Additionally, Python must be available on the remote "
"system, and be a version supported by Salt."
msgstr ""
"Per utilitzar Push mitjançant Salt SSH, heu de tenir el dimoni SSH executant-"
"se al client, i accessible pel dimoni [systemitem].salt-api. executant-se al "
"servidor {productname}.  A més, Python ha d'estar disponible en el sistema "
"remot, i ser una versió suportada per Salt."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:9
msgid ""
"{rhel}{nbsp}5, {centos}{nbsp}5, and earlier are not supported, as they use "
"unsupported versions of Python."
msgstr ""
"{rhel}{nbsp}5, {centos}{nbsp}5, i anteriors no són compatibles, ja que "
"utilitzen versions no admeses de Python."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Registering Clients with Push via Salt SSH"
msgstr "Procediment: Registre de clients amb Push a través de Salt SSH"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:11
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[Bootstrapping] and "
"complete the appropriate fields."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Bootstrapping] i completeu "
"els camps apropiats."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:12
msgid "Select an activation key with the Push via SSH contact method configured."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu una clau d'activació amb el mètode de contacte Push mitjançant "
"SSH configurat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:13
msgid ""
"For more information about activation keys, see "
"xref:client-configuration:activation-keys.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per obtenir més informació sobre les claus d'activació, vegeu xref:client-"
"configuration:activation-keys.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:14
msgid "Check the [systemitem]``Manage system completely via SSH`` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Marqueu la casella [systemitem].Gestioneu el sistema completament mitjançant "
"SSH.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:16
msgid ""
"Confirm that the system has been registered correctly by navigating to "
"menu:Systems[Overview]."
msgstr ""
"Confirmeu que el sistema s'ha registrat correctament navegant al "
"menú:Systems[Overview]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Available Parameters"
msgstr "Paràmetres disponibles"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:18
msgid ""
"When you are configuring Push via Salt SSH, you can modify parameters that "
"are used when a system is registered, including the host, activation key, "
"and password.  The password is used only for bootstrapping, it is not saved "
"anywhere.  All future SSH sessions are authorized via a key/certificate "
"pair.  These parameters are configured in menu:Systems[Bootstrapping]."
msgstr ""
"Quan esteu configurant Push via Salt SSH, podeu modificar els paràmetres que "
"s'utilitzen quan es registra un sistema, incloent-hi l'amfitrió, la clau "
"d'activació i la contrasenya.  La contrasenya només s'utilitza per arrencar, "
"no es desa enlloc.  Totes les futures sessions SSH s'autoritzen mitjançant "
"un parell de claus/certificats.  Aquests paràmetres es configuren al "
"menú:Systems[Bootstrapping]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:19
msgid ""
"You can also configure persistent parameters that are are used system-wide, "
"including the sudo user.  For more information on configuring the sudo user, "
"see xref:client-configuration:contact-methods-pushssh.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"També podeu configurar els paràmetres persistents que s'utilitzen a tot el "
"sistema, inclòs l'usuari sudo.  Per obtenir més informació sobre la "
"configuració de l'usuari sudo, vegeu xref:client-configuration:contact-"
"methods-pushssh.adoc[]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "Action Execution"
msgstr "Execució d'acció"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:21
msgid ""
"The Push via Salt SSH feature uses taskomatic to execute scheduled actions "
"using [command]``salt-ssh``.  The taskomatic job periodically checks for "
"scheduled actions and executes them.  Unlike Push via SSH on traditional "
"clients, the Push via Salt SSH feature executes a complete "
"[command]``salt-ssh`` call based on the scheduled action."
msgstr ""
"La característica Empeny a través de Salt SSH utilitza taskomatic per "
"executar accions planificades utilitzant [command].salt-ssh..  El treball "
"taskomatic comprova periòdicament les accions programades i les executa.  A "
"diferència de Push via SSH en clients tradicionals, la característica Push "
"via Salt SSH executa una crida completa [command]altsalt-ssh. basada en "
"l'acció programada."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:22
msgid ""
"By default, twenty Salt SSH actions can be executed at a time.  You can "
"increase the number of actions that can be executed in parallel, by adding "
"these lines to your configuration file, and adjusting the value of "
"``parallel_threads`` upwards.  We recommend you keep the number of parallel "
"actions low, to avoid problems:"
msgstr ""
"Per defecte, es poden executar vint accions Salt SSH alhora.  Podeu "
"augmentar el nombre d'accions que es poden executar en paral·lel, afegint "
"aquestes línies al fitxer de configuració i ajustant el valor de ."
"parallelthreads. cap amunt.  Us recomanem mantenir baix el nombre d'accions "
"paral·leles, per evitar problemes:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"taskomatic.com.redhat.rhn.taskomatic.task.SSHMinionActionExecutor.parallel_threads "
"= <number>\n"
"org.quartz.threadPool.threadCount = <value of parallel_threads + 20>\n"
msgstr ""
"taskomatic.com.redhat.rhn.taskomatic.task.SSHMinionActionExecutor.parallelthr"
"eads s <number>\n"
"org.quartz.threadPool.threadCount   <value of parallelthreads + 20>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:24
msgid ""
"This adjusts the number of actions that can run in parallel on any one "
"client and the total number of worker threads used by taskomatic.  If "
"actions needs to be run on multiple clients, actions are always executed "
"sequentially on each client."
msgstr ""
"Això ajusta el nombre d'accions que poden executar-se en paral·lel en "
"qualsevol client i el nombre total de fils de treball utilitzats per "
"taskomatic.  Si les accions s'han d'executar en múltiples clients, les "
"accions sempre s'executen seqüencialment en cada client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:25
msgid ""
"If the clients are connected through a proxy, you need to adjust the "
"``MaxSessions`` settings on the proxy.  In this case, set the number of "
"parallel connections to be three times the total number of clients."
msgstr ""
"Si els clients estan connectats a través d'un servidor intermediari, heu "
"d'ajustar la configuració de .MaxSessions. al servidor intermediari.  En "
"aquest cas, establir el nombre de connexions paral·leles a tres vegades el "
"nombre total de clients."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Future Features"
msgstr "Característiques futures"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:27
msgid ""
"There are some features that are not yet supported on Push via Salt SSH.  "
"These features do not work on Salt SSH clients:"
msgstr ""
"Hi ha algunes característiques que encara no estan suportades a Push via "
"Salt SSH.  Aquestes característiques no funcionen en clients de Salt SSH:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:28
msgid "OpenSCAP auditing"
msgstr "Auditoria OpenSCAP"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:29
msgid "Beacons, resulting in:"
msgstr "Beacons, resultant en:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:30
msgid ""
"Installing a package on a system using [command]``zypper`` does not invoke "
"the package refresh."
msgstr ""
"Instal·lar un paquet en un sistema utilitzant [command].zypper. no invoca "
"l'actualització del paquet."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:31
msgid ""
"Virtual Host functions (for example, a host to guests) does not work if the "
"virtual host system is Salt SSH-based."
msgstr ""
"Les funcions d'amfitrió virtual (per exemple, un amfitrió per a convidats) "
"no funcionen si el sistema d'amfitrió virtual està basat en Salt SSH."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:32
msgid ""
"For more information about Salt SSH, see "
"https://docs.saltstack.com/en/latest/topics/ssh/."
msgstr ""
"Per a més informació sobre Salt SSH, consulteu https://docs.saltstack.com/ca/"
"latest/topics/ssh/."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-traditional.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Contact Methods for Traditional Clients"
msgstr "Mètodes de contacte per a clients tradicionals"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-traditional.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Traditional clients can communicate with the {productname} Server using a "
"range of methods."
msgstr ""
"Els clients tradicionals poden comunicar-se amb el servidor {productname} "
"utilitzant una sèrie de mètodes."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-traditional.adoc:3
msgid ""
"The {productname} daemon ([command]``rhnsd``) runs on traditional client "
"systems and periodically connects with {productname} to check for new "
"updates and notifications."
msgstr ""
"El dimoni {productname} ([command].rhnsd.) s'executa en els sistemes de "
"clients tradicionals i es connecta periòdicament amb {productname} per "
"comprovar si hi ha actualitzacions i notificacions noves."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-traditional.adoc:4
msgid ""
"Push via SSH is used in environments where clients cannot reach the "
"{productname} Server directly.  In this environment, clients are located in "
"a firewall-protected zone called a DMZ.  No system within the DMZ is "
"authorized to open a connection to the internal network, including the "
"{productname} Server."
msgstr ""
"El Push via SSH s'utilitza en entorns on els clients no poden arribar "
"directament al servidor {productname}.  En aquest entorn, els clients es "
"troben en una zona protegida amb tallafoc anomenada DMZ.  Cap sistema dins "
"de la DMZ està autoritzat a obrir una connexió a la xarxa interna, inclòs el "
"servidor {productname}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-traditional.adoc:5
msgid ""
"OSAD is an alternative contact method between {productname} and traditional "
"clients.  OSAD allows traditional clients to execute scheduled actions "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"L'OSAD és un mètode de contacte alternatiu entre {productname} i clients "
"tradicionals.  OSAD permet als clients tradicionals executar accions "
"planificades immediatament."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-traditional.adoc:6
msgid ""
"Traditional clients will be deprecated with the next {productname} version "
"and will not be supported with future releases.  Be aware that when "
"migrating from traditional clients to Salt minions you do not have to delete "
"the registered clients before. You can just register them as Salt minions "
"and Salt will do the necessary steps with the traditional client. If you "
"already deleted the traditional client and the registration as Salt minion "
"is not possible anymore, see "
"xref:installation-and-upgrade:troubleshooting.adoc[Troubleshooting]."
msgstr ""
"Els clients tradicionals seran obsolets amb la propera versió de "
"{productname} i no seran compatibles amb versions futures.  Tingues en "
"compte que a l'hora de migrar de clients tradicionals a minions Salt no has "
"de suprimir els clients registrats abans. Només pots registrar-los com a "
"minions de Sal i Salt farà els passos necessaris amb el client tradicional. "
"Si ja heu suprimit el client tradicional i el registre com a minion Salt ja "
"no és possible, vegeu xref:installation-and-upgrade:troubleshooting."
"adoc[Troubleshooting]."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Custom System Information"
msgstr "Informació personalitzada del sistema"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:2
msgid ""
"You can include customized system information about your clients.  System "
"information is defined as key:value pairs, which can be assigned to "
"clients.  For example, you can define a key:value pair for a particular "
"processor, then assign that key to all clients that have that processor "
"installed.  Custom system information is categorized, and can be searched "
"using the {productname} {webui}."
msgstr ""
"Pots incloure informació personalitzada del sistema sobre els teus clients.  "
"La informació del sistema es defineix com parells clau:valor, que es poden "
"assignar als clients.  Per exemple, podeu definir un parell key:value per a "
"un processador en particular, i després assignar aquesta clau a tots els "
"clients que tenen aquest processador instal·lat.  La informació "
"personalitzada del sistema està categoritzada i es pot cercar utilitzant "
"{productname} {webui}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:3
msgid ""
"Before you begin, you need to create a key that allows you to store custom "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Abans de començar, heu de crear una clau que us permeti emmagatzemar "
"informació personalitzada."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:4
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Creating a Custom System Information Key"
msgstr "Procediment: Creació d'una clau d'informació personalitzada del sistema"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:5
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[Custom System Info], "
"and click btn:[Create Key]."
msgstr ""
"A la {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Informació del sistema "
"personalitzat], i feu clic a btn:[Crea clau]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:6
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Key Label`` field, add a name for your key.  Do not use "
"spaces.  For example, ``intel-x86_64-quadcore``."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Etiqueta de la clau., afegiu un nom per a la vostra clau.  "
"No facis servir espais.  Per exemple, .intel-x8664-quadcore.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:7
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Description`` field, provide any additional information "
"required."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Descripció., proporcioneu qualsevol informació addicional "
"requerida."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:8
msgid "Repeat for each key you require."
msgstr "Repeteix per a cada clau que necessitis."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:9
msgid ""
"For traditional clients, this information is stored in the {productname} "
"database.  For Salt clients, this information is stored in a Salt pillar.  "
"You can retrieve this information from a Salt client with a command such as:"
msgstr ""
"Per als clients tradicionals, aquesta informació s'emmagatzema a la base de "
"dades {productname}.  Per als clients de Salt, aquesta informació "
"s'emmagatzema en un pilar de Salt.  Podeu recuperar aquesta informació d'un "
"client de Salt amb una ordre com:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt $minionid pillar.get custom_info:key1\n"
msgstr "sal $minionid pilar.get custominfo:key1\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:11
msgid "This command will result in an output such as:"
msgstr "Aquesta ordre resultarà en una sortida com:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$minionid:\n"
"    val1\n"
msgstr ""
"$minionid:\n"
"    val1\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:13
msgid ""
"When you have created some custom system information keys, you can apply "
"them to clients."
msgstr ""
"Quan hàgiu creat algunes claus personalitzades d'informació del sistema, les "
"podeu aplicar als clients."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Applying Custom Information Keys to Clients"
msgstr ""
"Procediment: Aplicació de claus d'informació personalitzades als clients"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:15
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to [guimenu]``Systems``, click the "
"client to apply custom information to, and navigate to the "
"menu:Details[Custom Info] tab."
msgstr ""
"A la {productname} {webui}, navegueu a [guimenu].Sistemes., feu clic al "
"client per aplicar informació personalitzada i navegueu a la pestanya "
"menú:Detalls[Informació personalitzada]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:16
msgid "Click btn:[Create Value]."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Crea valor]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:17
msgid "Locate the value you want to apply, and click the key label."
msgstr ""
"Localitzeu el valor que voleu aplicar i feu clic a l'etiqueta de la clau."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:18
msgid "In the [guimenu]``Value`` field, provide any additional information."
msgstr "Al camp [guimenu].Valor., proporcioneu qualsevol informació addicional."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:19
msgid "Click btn:[Update Key] to apply the custom information to the client."
msgstr ""
"Feu clic a btn:[Update Key] per aplicar la informació personalitzada al "
"client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/custom-info.adoc:20
msgid ""
"For more information about configuration management, see "
"xref:client-configuration:configuration-management.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per obtenir més informació sobre la gestió de la configuració, vegeu xref"
":client-configuration:configuration-management.adoc[]."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Client Deletion"
msgstr "Supressió del client"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you need to remove a client from your {productname} Server, you can use "
"the {webui} to delete it.  This procedure works for both traditional and "
"Salt clients."
msgstr ""
"Si necessiteu eliminar un client del vostre servidor {productname}, podeu "
"utilitzar el {webui} per suprimir-lo.  Aquest procediment funciona tant per "
"a clients tradicionals com per a clients de Salt."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:3
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Deleting a Client"
msgstr "Procediment: Suprimir un client"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:4
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[System List] and "
"select the client to delete."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Llista de sistemes] i "
"seleccioneu el client a suprimir."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:5
msgid "Click btn:[Delete System]."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Suprimeix el sistema]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:6
msgid "Check the details and click btn:[Delete Profile] to confirm."
msgstr ""
"Comproveu els detalls i feu clic a btn:[Suprimeix el perfil] per a confirmar-"
"ho."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:7
msgid ""
"For Salt clients, {productname} attempts to clean up additional "
"configuration.  If the client cannot be contacted, you are given the option "
"to cancel the deletion, or delete the client without cleaning up the "
"configuration files."
msgstr ""
"Per als clients de Salt, {productname} intenta netejar la configuració "
"addicional.  Si no es pot contactar amb el client, se li dona l'opció de "
"cancel·lar la supressió, o eliminar el client sense netejar els fitxers de "
"configuració."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:8
msgid ""
"You can also delete multiple clients using the system set manager.  For more "
"information about the system set manager, see "
"xref:client-configuration:system-set-manager.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"També podeu suprimir diversos clients utilitzant el gestor de conjunts de "
"sistemes.  Per obtenir més informació sobre el gestor de conjunts de "
"sistemes, vegeu xref:client-configuration:system-set-manager.adoc[]."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:9
msgid ""
"It is not possible to automatically clean up a a traditional client after "
"deleting it. You have to take care of this yourself. Furthermore cleaning up "
"a Salt minion does not remove Salt itself."
msgstr ""
"No és possible netejar automàticament un client tradicional després de "
"suprimir-lo. T'has d'encarregar d'això tu mateix. A més, la neteja d'un "
"minió de sal no treu la sal en si."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Normally you migrate a traditional client to a Salt minion without deleting "
"the client. Salt automatically detects that you have a traditional client "
"and does the necessary changes itself. But if you already deleted the "
"traditional client and want to register it as a Salt minion again, see "
"xref:installation-and-upgrade:troubleshooting.adoc[Troubleshooting]."
msgstr ""
"Normalment migreu un client tradicional a un minion de Salt sense eliminar "
"el client. Salt detecta automàticament que tens un client tradicional i fa "
"els canvis necessaris per si mateix. Però si ja heu suprimit el client "
"tradicional i voleu tornar a registrar-lo com a minion Salt, vegeu xref"
":installation-and-upgrade:troubleshooting.adoc[Troubleshooting]."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/gpg-keys.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "GPG Keys"
msgstr "Tecles GPG"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/gpg-keys.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Clients use GPG keys to check the authenticity of software packages before "
"they are installed.  Only trusted software can be installed on clients."
msgstr ""
"Els clients utilitzen claus GPG per comprovar l'autenticitat dels paquets de "
"programari abans que s'instal·lin.  Només es pot instal·lar programari de "
"confiança als clients."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/gpg-keys.adoc:3
msgid ""
"In most cases, you do not need to adjust the GPG settings to be able to "
"install software on your clients."
msgstr ""
"En la majoria dels casos, no cal que ajusteu la configuració de GPG per a "
"poder instal·lar programari als vostres clients."

#
#
#
#
#
#. From Ref Guide, needs editing. --LKB 2020-09-08
#. Lists keys and certificates available for inclusion in {kickstart} profiles and provides a means to create new ones.
#. This is especially important for customers of {productname} or the Proxy Server because systems kickstarted by them must have the server key imported into {productname} and associated with the relevant {kickstart} profiles.
#. Import a profile by creating a new key on this page and then make the profile association in the [guimenu]``GPG and SSL keys`` subtab of the [guimenu]``Autoinstallation Details`` page.
#. To create a key or certificate, click the [guimenu]``Create Stored Key/Cert`` link in the upper-right corner of the page.
#. Enter a description, select the type, upload the file, and click the btn:[Update Key] button.
#. A unique description is required.
#. [IMPORTANT]
#. ====
#. The GPG key you upload to {productname} must be in ASCII format.
#. Using a GPG key in binary format causes anaconda, and therefore the {kickstart} process, to fail.
#. ====
#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Package Management"
msgstr "Gestió de paquets"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:2
msgid "Clients use packages to install, uninstall, and upgrade software."
msgstr ""
"Els clients utilitzen paquets per instal·lar, desinstal·lar i actualitzar "
"programari."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:3
msgid ""
"To manage packages on a client, navigate to [guimenu]``Systems``, click the "
"client to manage, and navigate to the menu:Systems[Software > Packages] "
"subtab.  The options available in this section vary depending on the type of "
"client you have selected, and its current channel subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Per gestionar paquets en un client, navegueu a [guimenu].Sistemes., feu clic "
"al client per gestionar-los i navegueu a la subpestanya menú:Sistemes["
"Software . Paquets].  Les opcions disponibles en aquesta secció varien en "
"funció del tipus de client que hagis seleccionat, i de les seves "
"subscripcions al canal actual."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:4
msgid ""
"When packages are installed or upgraded, licenses or EULAs are automatically "
"accepted."
msgstr ""
"Quan els paquets s'instal·len o s'actualitzen, les llicències o els EULA "
"s'accepten automàticament."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:5
msgid ""
"Most package management actions can be added to action chains.  For more "
"about action chains, see xref:reference:schedule/action-chains.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"La majoria de les accions de gestió de paquets es poden afegir a les cadenes "
"d'acció.  Per obtenir més informació sobre les cadenes d'acció, vegeu "
"xref:reference:schedule/action-chains.adoc[]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Verify Packages"
msgstr "Verifica els paquets"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:7
msgid ""
"You can check that packages you have installed on a client match the current "
"state of the database they were installed from.  The metadata of the "
"installed package is compared to information in the database, including the "
"file checksum, file size, permissions, owner, group, and type."
msgstr ""
"Podeu comprovar que els paquets que heu instal·lat en un client coincideixen "
"amb l'estat actual de la base de dades des de la qual s'han instal·lat.  Les "
"metadades del paquet instal·lat es comparen amb la informació de la base de "
"dades, inclosa la suma de verificació de fitxers, la mida del fitxer, els "
"permisos, el propietari, el grup i el tipus."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Verifying Installed Packages"
msgstr "Procediment: Verificació dels paquets instal·lats"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:9
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to [guimenu]``Systems``, click the "
"client the package is installed on, and navigate to the "
"menu:Systems[Software > Packages > Verify] subtab."
msgstr ""
"A la {productname} {webui}, navegueu a [guimenu].Systems., feu clic al "
"client on està instal·lat el paquet i navegueu al menú:Systems[Software . "
"Packages . Verify] subtab."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Select the packages you want to verify and click btn:[Verify Selected "
"Packages]."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu els paquets que voleu verificar i feu clic a btn:[Verifica els "
"paquets seleccionats]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:11
msgid ""
"When the verification is complete, navigate to menu:Systems[Events > "
"History] to see the results."
msgstr ""
"Quan la verificació estigui completada, navegueu a menú:Sistemes["
"Esdeveniments . Historial] per a veure els resultats."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Compare Packages"
msgstr "Compara els paquets"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:13
msgid ""
"You can compare the packages installed on a client with a stored profile, or "
"with packages installed on another client.  When the comparison is made, you "
"can choose to modify the selected client to match."
msgstr ""
"Podeu comparar els paquets instal·lats en un client amb un perfil "
"emmagatzemat, o amb els paquets instal·lats en un altre client.  Quan es "
"faci la comparació, podeu triar modificar el client seleccionat perquè "
"coincideixi."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:14
msgid ""
"To compare packages against a profile, you need to have stored a profile.  "
"Profiles are created from the packages on a currently installed client.  "
"When the profile has been created, you can use it to install more clients "
"with the same packages installed."
msgstr ""
"Per comparar paquets amb un perfil, heu de tenir emmagatzemat un perfil.  "
"Els perfils es creen a partir dels paquets en un client instal·lat "
"actualment.  Quan s'ha creat el perfil, podeu utilitzar-lo per instal·lar "
"més clients amb els mateixos paquets instal·lats."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Creating a Stored Profile"
msgstr "Procediment: Creació d'un perfil emmagatzemat"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:16
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to [guimenu]``Systems``, click the "
"client to base your profile off, and navigate to the menu:Systems[Software > "
"Packages > Profiles] subtab."
msgstr ""
"A la {productname} {webui}, navegueu a [guimenu].Sistemes., feu clic al "
"client per a desactivar el vostre perfil i navegueu al menú:Sistemes["
"Software . Paquets . Perfils] subpestanya."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:17
msgid "Click btn:[Create System Profile]."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Crea el perfil del sistema]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:18
msgid "Type a name and description for your profile and click btn:[Create Profile]."
msgstr ""
"Escriviu un nom i una descripció per al vostre perfil i feu clic a btn:[Crea "
"un perfil]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Comparing Client Packages"
msgstr "Procediment: Comparació de paquets de clients"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:20
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to [guimenu]``Systems``, click the "
"client to compare, and navigate to the menu:Systems[Software > Packages > "
"Profiles] subtab."
msgstr ""
"A la {productname} {webui}, navegueu a [guimenu].Sistemes., feu clic al "
"client per comparar i navegueu al menú:Sistemes[Software . Paquets . Perfils]"
" subpestanya."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:21
msgid ""
"To compare with a stored profile, select the profile and click "
"btn:[Compare]."
msgstr ""
"Per comparar amb un perfil emmagatzemat, seleccioneu el perfil i feu clic a "
"btn:[Compara]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:22
msgid ""
"To compare with another client, select the client name and click "
"btn:[Compare] to see a list of differences between the two clients."
msgstr ""
"Per comparar amb un altre client, seleccioneu el nom del client i feu clic a "
"btn:[Compare] per veure una llista de diferències entre els dos clients."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/package-management.adoc:23
msgid ""
"Check packages you want to install on the selected client, uncheck packages "
"you want to remove, and click btn:[Sync Packages to]."
msgstr ""
"Comproveu els paquets que voleu instal·lar al client seleccionat, desmarqueu "
"els paquets que voleu eliminar i feu clic a btn:[Sincronitza els paquets a]."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Patch Management"
msgstr "Gestió de pedaços"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:2
msgid ""
"You can use custom patches within your organization to manage clients.  This "
"allows you to issue patch alerts for packages in custom channels, schedule "
"patch installation, and manage patches across organizations."
msgstr ""
"Pots utilitzar pedaços personalitzats dins de la teva organització per "
"gestionar clients.  Això permet emetre alertes de pedaç per als paquets en "
"canals personalitzats, programar la instal·lació de pedaç i gestionar "
"pedaços entre les organitzacions."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:3
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create Patches"
msgstr "Crea pedaços"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:4
msgid ""
"To use a custom patch, you need to create the patch, add packages to it and "
"add it to one or more channels."
msgstr ""
"Per utilitzar un pedaç personalitzat, heu de crear el pedaç, afegir-hi "
"paquets i afegir-lo a un o més canals."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Creating a Custom Patch"
msgstr "Procediment: Creació d'un pedaço personalitzat"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:6
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Patches[Manage Patches], "
"click btn:[Create Patch]."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Patches[Manage Patches], feu clic "
"a btn:[Create Patch]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:7
msgid "In the ``Create Patch`` section, use these details:"
msgstr "A la secció  theCreate Patch the, utilitzeu aquests detalls:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:8
msgid "In the ``Synopsis`` field, type a short description of the patch."
msgstr "En el camp .Sinopsi., escriviu una breu descripció del pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:9
msgid "In the ``Advisory`` field, type a label for the patch."
msgstr "Al camp .Assessoria., escriviu una etiqueta per al pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:10
msgid ""
"We recommend you devise a naming convention for your organization to make "
"patch management easier."
msgstr ""
"Et recomanem que dissenyis una convenció de naming per a la teva "
"organització per facilitar la gestió de patch."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:11
msgid "In the ``Advisory Release`` field, enter a release number for your patch."
msgstr ""
"Al camp .Advisory Release., introduïu un número de llançament per al vostre "
"pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:12
msgid "For example, if this is the first version of this patch, use ``1``."
msgstr ""
"Per exemple, si aquesta és la primera versió d'aquest pedaç, utilitzeu 11.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:13
msgid "In the ``Advisory Type`` field, select the type of patch to use."
msgstr ""
"Al camp .Tipus d'assessorament., seleccioneu el tipus de pedaç a utilitzar."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:14
msgid "For example, ``Bug Fix Advisory`` for a patch that fixes errors."
msgstr ""
"Per exemple, .Bug Fix Advisory. per a un pedaç que corregeix els errors."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:15
msgid ""
"If you selected an advisory type of ``Security Advisory``, in the ``Advisory "
"Severity`` field, select the severity level to use."
msgstr ""
"Si heu seleccionat un tipus d'assessorament de .Security Advisory., en el "
"camp .Severity Assessora., seleccioneu el nivell de gravetat a utilitzar."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:16
msgid "In the ``Product`` field, type the name of the product this patch refers to."
msgstr ""
"En el camp .Producte., escriviu el nom del producte al qual es refereix "
"aquest pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:17
msgid "OPTIONAL: In the ``Author`` field, type the name of the author of the patch."
msgstr "OPCIONAL: En el camp .Autor., escriviu el nom de l'autor del pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:18
msgid ""
"Complete the ``Topic``, ``Description``, and ``Solution`` fields with "
"further information about the patch."
msgstr ""
"Completeu els camps .Topic., .Description. i .Solution. amb més informació "
"sobre el pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:19
msgid ""
"OPTIONAL: In the ``Bugs`` section, specify the information of any related "
"bugs, using these details:"
msgstr ""
"OPCIONAL: A la secció  theBugs the, especifiqueu la informació de qualsevol "
"error relacionat, utilitzant aquests detalls:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:20
msgid "In the ``ID`` field, enter the bug number."
msgstr "Al camp .ID., introduïu el número d'error."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:21
msgid "In the ``Summary`` field, type a short description of the bug."
msgstr "En el camp .Summary., escriviu una breu descripció de l'error."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:22
msgid "In the ``Bugzilla URL`` field, type the address of the bug."
msgstr "En el camp .URL de Bugzilla., escriviu l'adreça de l'error."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:23
msgid "In the ``Keywords`` field, type any keywords related to the bug."
msgstr ""
"En el camp .Keywords., escriviu qualsevol paraula clau relacionada amb "
"l'error."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:24
msgid "Use a comma between each keyword."
msgstr "Utilitza una coma entre cada paraula clau."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:25
msgid ""
"Complete the ``References`` and ``Notes`` fields with further information "
"about the bug."
msgstr ""
"Completeu els camps .Referències. i .Notes. amb més informació sobre l'error."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:26
msgid "Select one or more channels to add the new patch to."
msgstr "Seleccioneu un o més canals per afegir el pedaç nou."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:27
msgid "Click btn:[Create Patch]."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Crea un pedaço]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:28
msgid ""
"You can also create patches by cloning an existing one.  Cloning preserves "
"package associations and simplifies issuing patches."
msgstr ""
"També podeu crear pedaços clonant un existent.  La clonació preserva les "
"associacions de paquets i simplifica l'emissió de pedaços."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Cloning Patches"
msgstr "Procediment: Pedaços de clonació"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:30
msgid "In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Patches[Clone Patches]."
msgstr "A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Patches[Clone Patches]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:31
msgid ""
"In the ``View patches potentially applicable to:`` field, select the "
"software channel for the patch you want to clone."
msgstr ""
"Al camp .Veure pedaços potencialment aplicables a:., seleccioneu el canal de "
"programari per al pedaç que voleu clonar."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:32
msgid ""
"Select the patch or patches you want to clone, and click btn:[Clone "
"Patches]."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu el pedaç o els pedaços que voleu clonar i feu clic a btn:[Clone "
"Patches]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:33
msgid "Select one or more channels to add the cloned patch to."
msgstr "Seleccioneu un o més canals per afegir el pedaç clonat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:34
msgid "Confirm the details to begin the clone."
msgstr "Confirmeu els detalls per començar el clon."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:35
msgid "When you have created a patch, you can assign packages to it."
msgstr "Quan hàgiu creat un pedaç, podeu assignar-hi paquets."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Assigning Packages to a Patch"
msgstr "Procediment: Assignació de paquets a un pedaço"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:37
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Patches[Manage Patches], and "
"click the the advisory name of the patch to see the patch details."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Patches[Manage Patches], i feu "
"clic al nom d'assessorament del pedaç per veure els detalls del pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:38
msgid "Navigate to the menu:Packages[Add] tab."
msgstr "Navega al menú:Packages[Afegeix] pestanya."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:39
msgid ""
"In the ``Channel`` field, select the software channel that contains the "
"packages you want to assign to the patch, and click btn:[View Packages]."
msgstr ""
"Al camp ].Channel]., seleccioneu el canal de programari que conté els "
"paquets que voleu assignar al pedaç i feu clic a btn:[Veure paquets]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:40
msgid ""
"You can select ``All managed packages`` to see the available packages in all "
"channels."
msgstr ""
"Podeu seleccionar .Tots els paquets gestionats. per veure els paquets "
"disponibles a tots els canals."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:41
msgid "Check the packages you want to include, and click btn:[Add Packages]."
msgstr ""
"Comproveu els paquets que voleu incloure i feu clic a btn:[Afegeix paquets]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:42
msgid ""
"Confirm the details of the packages, and click btn:[Confirm] to assign them "
"to the patch."
msgstr ""
"Confirmeu els detalls dels paquets i feu clic a btn:[Confirm] per a assignar-"
"los al pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:43
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:Packages[List/Remove] tab to check that the packages "
"have been assigned correctly."
msgstr ""
"Navega a la pestanya menú:Packages[Llista/Elimina] per a comprovar que els "
"paquets s'han assignat correctament."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:44
msgid ""
"When packages are assigned to a patch, the patch cache is updated to reflect "
"the changes.  The cache update might take a couple of minutes."
msgstr ""
"Quan els paquets s'assignen a un pedaç, la memòria cau del pedaç "
"s'actualitza per reflectir els canvis.  L'actualització de la memòria cau "
"pot trigar un parell de minuts."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:45
msgid ""
"If you need to change the details of an existing patch, you can do so from "
"the [guimenu]``Patches Management`` page."
msgstr ""
"Si necessiteu canviar els detalls d'un pedaç existent, podeu fer-ho des de "
"la pàgina [guimenu].Gestió de mapes.."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Editing and Deleting Existing Patch Alerts"
msgstr "Procediment: Edició i supressió de les alertes de pedaços existents"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:47
msgid "In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Patches[Manage Patches]."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Patches[Gestionar els pedaços]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:48
msgid "Click the advisory name of the patch to see the patch details."
msgstr "Feu clic al nom de l'avís del pedaç per veure els detalls del pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:49
msgid "Make the changes as required, and click btn:[Update Patch]."
msgstr ""
"Feu els canvis segons sigui necessari, i feu clic a btn:[Actualitza Pedaç]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:50
msgid ""
"To delete a patch, select the patch in the [guimenu]``Patches Management`` "
"page, and click btn:[Delete Patches]."
msgstr ""
"Per a suprimir un pedaç, seleccioneu el pedaç a la pàgina [guimenu]].Gestió "
"de les pestanyes]. i feu clic a btn:[Elimina les pedaços]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:51
msgid "Deleting patches might take a few minutes."
msgstr "Eliminar pedaços pot trigar uns minuts."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "Apply Patches to Clients"
msgstr "Aplica pedaços als clients"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:53
msgid ""
"When a patch is ready, you can apply it to clients either singly, or with "
"other patches."
msgstr ""
"Quan un pedaç està a punt, pots aplicar-lo als clients individualment o amb "
"altres pedaços."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:54
msgid ""
"Each package within a patch is part of one or more channels.  If the client "
"is not subscribed to the channel, the update is not installed."
msgstr ""
"Cada paquet d'un pedaç forma part d'un o més canals.  Si el client no està "
"subscrit al canal, l'actualització no està instal·lada."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:55
msgid ""
"If the client has a more recent version of a package already installed, the "
"update is not installed.  If the client has an older version of the package "
"installed, the package is upgraded."
msgstr ""
"Si el client té una versió més recent d'un paquet ja instal·lat, "
"l'actualització no està instal·lada.  Si el client té instal·lada una versió "
"antiga del paquet, el paquet s'actualitza."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Applying All Applicable Patches"
msgstr "Procediment: Aplicar tots els pedaços aplicables"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:57
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[Overview] and select "
"the client you want to update."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Sistemes[Vista general] i "
"seleccioneu el client que voleu actualitzar."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:58
msgid "Navigate to the menu:Software[Patches] tab."
msgstr "Navega a la pestanya menú:Software[Patches]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:59
msgid "Click btn:[Select All] to select all applicable patches."
msgstr ""
"Feu clic a btn:[Selecciona-ho tot] per a seleccionar tots els pedaços "
"aplicables."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:60
msgid "Click btn:[Apply Patches] to update the client."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Aplica els pedaços] per actualitzar el client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:61
msgid ""
"If you are signed in with Administrator privileges, you can also perform "
"larger batch upgrades for clients."
msgstr ""
"Si heu iniciat sessió amb privilegis d'administrador, també podeu realitzar "
"actualitzacions per lots més grans per als clients."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Applying a Single Patch to Multiple Clients"
msgstr "Procediment: Aplicació d'un únic pedaço a múltiples clients"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:63
msgid "In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Patches[Patch List]."
msgstr "A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Patches[Patch List]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:64
msgid ""
"Locate the patch you want to apply, and click the number under the "
"``Systems`` column for that patch."
msgstr ""
"Localitzeu el pedaç que voleu aplicar i feu clic al número que hi ha a la "
"columna .Sistemes. per a aquest pedaç."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:65
msgid ""
"Select the clients you want to apply the patch to, and click btn:[Apply "
"Patches]."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu els clients als quals voleu aplicar el pedaç i feu clic a btn:["
"Aplica els pedaços]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:66
#, no-wrap
msgid " Confirm the list of clients to perform the update."
msgstr " Confirmeu la llista de clients per a realitzar l'actualització."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Applying Multiple Patches to Multiple Clients"
msgstr "Procediment: Aplicació de múltiples pedaços a múltiples clients"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:68
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[Overview] and check "
"the clients you want to update to add them to the system set manager."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Overview] i comproveu els "
"clients que voleu actualitzar per afegir-los al gestor de conjunts del "
"sistema."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:69
msgid ""
"Navigate to menu:Systems[System Set Manager] and naviagte to the "
"[guimenu]``Patches`` tab."
msgstr ""
"Navega al menú:Systems[System Set Manager] i naviagte a la pestanya [guimenu]"
".Patches.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:70
msgid ""
"Select the patches you want to apply to the clients and click btn:[Apply "
"Patches]."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu els pedaços que voleu aplicar als clients i feu clic a btn:["
"Aplica els pedaços]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:71
msgid "Schedule a date and time for the update to occur, and click btn:[Confirm]."
msgstr ""
"Planifiqueu una data i hora perquè es produeixi l'actualització i feu clic a "
"btn:[Confirm]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:72
msgid ""
"To check the progress of the update, navigate to menu:Schedule[Pending "
"Actions]."
msgstr ""
"Per a comprovar el progrés de l'actualització, navegueu al menú:Schedule["
"Accions pendents]."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/patch-management.adoc:73
msgid ""
"Scheduled package updates are installed using the contact method configured "
"for each client.  For more information, see "
"xref:client-configuration:contact-methods-intro.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Les actualitzacions de paquets planificades s'instal·len utilitzant el "
"mètode de contacte configurat per a cada client.  Per a més informació, "
"vegeu xref:client-configuration:contact-methods-intro.adoc[]."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power Management"
msgstr "Gestió d'energia"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:2
msgid ""
"You can power on, power off, and reboot clients using the {productname} "
"{webui}."
msgstr ""
"Podeu activar, apagar i reiniciar clients utilitzant {productname} {webui}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:3
msgid ""
"This feature uses either the IPMI or Redfish protocol and is managed using a "
"Cobbler profile.  The selected client must have a power management "
"controller supporting one of these protocols."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta característica utilitza el protocol IPMI o Redfish i es gestiona "
"utilitzant un perfil Cobbler.  El client seleccionat ha de disposar d'un "
"controlador de gestió d'energia que suporti un d'aquests protocols."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:4
msgid ""
"For Redfish, ensure you can establish a valid SSL connection between the "
"client and the {productname} Server.  You must have trusted the certificate "
"authority used to sign the SSL Server Certificate of the Redfish management "
"controller.  The CA certificate must be in ``.pem`` format, and stored on "
"the {productname} Server at [path]``/etc/pki/trust/anchors/``.  When you "
"have saved the certificate, run [command]``update-ca-certificate``."
msgstr ""
"Per a Redfish, assegureu-vos que podeu establir una connexió SSL vàlida "
"entre el client i el servidor {productname}.  Heu d'haver confiat en "
"l'autoritat certificadora utilitzada per signar el Certificat de Servidor "
"SSL del controlador de gestió Redfish.  El certificat de la CA ha d'estar en "
"format ..pem. i s'ha d'emmagatzemar al servidor {productname} a [path]./etc/"
"pki/trust/anchors/..  Quan hàgiu desat el certificat, executeu [command"
"].update-ca-certificate.."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Enabling Power Management"
msgstr "Procediment: Activació de la gestió d'energia"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:6
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[Systems List], select "
"the client you want to manage, and navigate to the menu:Provisioning[Power "
"Management] tab."
msgstr ""
"A la {productname} {webui}, navegueu a menu:Systems[Systems List], "
"seleccioneu el client que voleu gestionar i navegueu a la pestanya "
"menu:Provisioning[Power Management]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:7
msgid "In the [guimenu]``Type`` field, select the power management protocol to use."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Tipus., seleccioneu el protocol de gestió d'energia a "
"utilitzar."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:8
msgid ""
"Complete the details for the power management server, and click the "
"appropriate button for the action to take, or click btn:[Save only] to save "
"the details without taking any action."
msgstr ""
"Completeu els detalls del servidor de gestió d'energia i feu clic al botó "
"apropiat per a l'acció a realitzar, o feu clic a btn:[Desa només] per a "
"desar els detalls sense prendre cap acció."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:9
msgid ""
"You can apply power management actions to multiple clients at the same time "
"by adding them to the system set manager.  For more information about using "
"the system set manager, see "
"xref:client-configuration:system-set-manager.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Podeu aplicar accions de gestió d'energia a múltiples clients al mateix "
"temps, afegint-les al gestor de conjunts de sistemes.  Per obtenir més "
"informació sobre l'ús del gestor de conjunts de sistemes, vegeu xref:client-"
"configuration:system-set-manager.adoc[]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power Management and Cobbler"
msgstr "Gestió d'energia i rebost"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:11
msgid ""
"The first time you use a power management feature, a Cobbler system record "
"is automatically created, if one does not yet exist for the client.  These "
"automatically created system records are not bootable from the network, and "
"include a reference to a dummy system image.  This is needed because Cobbler "
"does not currently support system records without profiles or images."
msgstr ""
"La primera vegada que utilitzeu una funció de gestió d'energia, es crea "
"automàticament un registre del sistema Cobbler, si encara no existeix per al "
"client.  Aquests registres de sistema creats automàticament no es poden "
"arrencar des de la xarxa, i inclouen una referència a una imatge de sistema "
"fictícia.  Això és necessari perquè Cobbler no admet registres del sistema "
"sense perfils o imatges."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/power-management.adoc:12
msgid ""
"Cobbler power management uses fence-agent tools to support protocols other "
"than IPMI.  Only IPMI and Redfish protocols are supported by {productname}.  "
"You can configure your client to use other protocols by adding the "
"fence-agent names as a comma-separated list to the "
"[option]``java.power_management.types`` configuration parameter in the "
"[path]``rhn.conf`` configuration files."
msgstr ""
"La gestió d'energia de Cobbler utilitza eines d'agent de tanca per donar "
"suport a protocols diferents de l'IPMI.  Només els protocols IPMI i Redfish "
"són compatibles amb {productname}.  Podeu configurar el vostre client per "
"utilitzar altres protocols afegint els noms dels agents de tanca com una "
"llista separada per comes al paràmetre de configuració [option]."
"java.powermanagement.types. als fitxers de configuració [path].rhn.conf.."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/products.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Software Products"
msgstr "Productes de programari"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/products.adoc:2
msgid ""
"In {productname}, software is made available in products.  Your {suse} "
"subscription allows you to access a range of different products, which you "
"can browse and select in the {productname} {webui} by navigating to "
"menu:Admin[Setup Wizard > Products]."
msgstr ""
"A {productname}, el programari està disponible als productes.  La vostra "
"subscripció a {suse} us permet accedir a una sèrie de productes diferents, "
"que podeu navegar i seleccionar a {productname} {webui} navegant al "
"menú:Admin[Auxiliar de configuració ]. Productes]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/products.adoc:3
msgid ""
"Products contain any number of software channels.  Click the `Show product's "
"channels` icon to see the channels included in the product.  When you have "
"added a product and synchronized successfully, you have access to the "
"channels provided by the product, and can use the packages in the product on "
"your {productname} Server and clients."
msgstr ""
"Els productes contenen qualsevol nombre de canals de programari.  Feu clic a "
"la icona .Mostra els canals del producte. per a veure els canals inclosos en "
"el producte.  Quan hàgiu afegit un producte i sincronitzat correctament, "
"teniu accés als canals proporcionats pel producte, i podeu utilitzar els "
"paquets del producte al vostre servidor i clients {productname}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/products.adoc:4
msgid "For more information, see xref:installation-and-upgrade:setup-wizard.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per a més informació, vegeu xref:installation-and-upgrade:setup-wizard."
"adoc[]."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Register Clients with a Bootstrap Script"
msgstr "Registra clients amb un script Bootstrap"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Registering clients with a bootstrap script gives you control over "
"parameters, and can help if you have to register a large number of clients "
"at once.  This method works for both Salt and traditional clients."
msgstr ""
"Registrar clients amb un script bootstrap et dona control sobre paràmetres, "
"i pot ajudar si has de registrar un gran nombre de clients alhora.  Aquest "
"mètode funciona tant per a clients de Salt com tradicionals."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:3
msgid ""
"To register clients using a bootstrap script, we recommend you create a "
"template bootstrap script to begin, which can then be copied and modified.  "
"The bootstrap script you create is executed on the client when it is "
"registered, and ensures all the necessary packages are deployed to the "
"client.  There are some parameters contained in the bootstrap script, which "
"ensure the client system can be assigned to its base channel, including "
"activation keys and GPG keys."
msgstr ""
"Per registrar clients utilitzant un script bootstrap, us recomanem crear una "
"plantilla d'script bootstrap per començar, que després es pot copiar i "
"modificar.  L'script bootstrap que creeu s'executa al client quan està "
"registrat, i assegura que tots els paquets necessaris es despleguen al "
"client.  Hi ha alguns paràmetres continguts en l'script bootstrap, que "
"garanteixen que el sistema client es pugui assignar al seu canal base, "
"incloses les claus d'activació i les claus GPG."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:4
msgid ""
"It is important that you check the repository information carefully, to "
"ensure it matches the base channel repository.  If the repository "
"information does not match exactly, the bootstrap script cannot download the "
"correct packages."
msgstr ""
"És important que comproveu la informació del repositori amb cura, per "
"assegurar-vos que coincideix amb el repositori del canal base.  Si la "
"informació del repositori no coincideix exactament, l'script bootstrap no "
"pot baixar els paquets correctes."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:5
msgid ""
"A bootstrap repository is needed for all clients.  It is automatically "
"created and regenerated on the SUSE Manager Server when products are "
"synchronized.  A bootstrap repository includes packages for installing Salt "
"on clients and for registering Salt or traditional clients.  For more "
"information about creating a bootstrap repository, see "
"xref:client-configuration:bootstrap-repository.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Es necessita un repositori d'arrencada per a tots els clients.  Es crea i "
"regenera automàticament al servidor SUSE Manager quan es sincronitzen els "
"productes.  Un repositori bootstrap inclou paquets per instal·lar Salt en "
"clients i per registrar Salt o clients tradicionals.  Per a més informació "
"sobre com crear un repositori bootstrap, vegeu xref:client-configuration"
":bootstrap-repository.adoc[]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "GPG Keys and Uyuni Client Tools"
msgstr "Claus GPG i eines de client Uyuni"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:7
msgid ""
"The GPG key used by Uyuni Client Tools is not trusted by default.  When you "
"create your bootstrap script, add a path to the file containing the public "
"key fingerprint with the [systemitem]``ORG_GPG_KEY`` parameter."
msgstr ""
"La clau GPG utilitzada per Uyuni Client Tools no és de confiança per "
"defecte.  Quan creeu l'script bootstrap, afegiu un camí al fitxer que conté "
"l'empremta digital de la clau pública amb el paràmetre [systemitem]."
"ORGGPGKEY.."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "openSUSE Leap 15 and SLES 15 and Python 3"
msgstr "openSUSE Leap 15 i SLES 15 i Python 3"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:9
msgid ""
"openSUSE Leap 15 and SLE 15 use Python 3 by default.  Bootstrap scripts "
"based on Python 2 must be re-created for openSUSE Leap 15 and SLE 15 "
"systems.  If you register openSUSE Leap 15 or SLE 15 systems using Python 2, "
"the bootstrap script fails."
msgstr ""
"openSUSE Leap 15 i SLE 15 utilitzen Python 3 per defecte.  Els scripts "
"Bootstrap basats en Python 2 s'han de tornar a crear per als sistemes "
"openSUSE Leap 15 i SLE 15.  Si registreu sistemes openSUSE Leap 15 o SLE 15 "
"utilitzant Python 2, falla l'script bootstrap."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create a Bootstrap Script from {webui}"
msgstr "Crea un script Bootstrap des de {webui}"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:11
msgid ""
"You can use the {productname} {webui} to create an editable bootstrap "
"script."
msgstr ""
"Podeu utilitzar el {productname} {webui} per crear un script d'arrencada "
"editable."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Creating a Bootstrap Script"
msgstr "Procediment: Creació d'un script Bootstrap"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:13
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Admin[Manager Configuration > "
"Bootstrap Script]."
msgstr ""
"A la {productname} {webui}, navegueu a menu:Admin[Manager Configuration ]. "
"Bootstrap Script]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:14
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``SUSE Manager Configuration - Bootstrap`` dialog, uncheck "
"the [guimenu]``Bootstrap using Salt`` checkbox if you are installing a "
"traditional client."
msgstr ""
"Al diàleg [guimenu].Configuració del gestor d'USEs - Bootstrap., desmarqueu "
"la casella de selecció [guimenu].Bootstrap utilitzant Salt. si esteu instal·"
"lant un client tradicional."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:15
msgid "For Salt clients, leave it checked."
msgstr "Per als clients de Salt, deixeu-ho comprovat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:16
msgid ""
"The required fields are pre-populated with values derived from previous "
"installation steps."
msgstr ""
"Els camps requerits estan pre-poblats amb valors derivats de passos d'instal·"
"lació anteriors."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:17
msgid ""
"For details on each setting, see "
"xref:reference:admin/bootstrap-script.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per obtenir més detalls sobre cada paràmetre, vegeu xref:reference:admin/"
"bootstrap-script.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:18
msgid "Click btn:[Update] to create the script."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Actualitza] per a crear l'script."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:19
msgid ""
"The bootstrap script is generated and stored on the server in the "
"[path]``/srv/www/htdocs/pub/bootstrap`` directory."
msgstr ""
"L'script bootstrap es genera i s'emmagatzema al servidor al directori "
"[path]./srv/www/htdocs/pub/bootstrap.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:20
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can access the bootstrap script over HTTPS.  Replace "
"``example.com`` with the host name of your {productname} Server:"
msgstr ""
"Alternativament, podeu accedir a l'script bootstrap a través d'HTTPS.  "
"Reemplaça  theexample.com the amb el nom de l'amfitrió del vostre servidor "
"{productname}:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://<example.com>/pub/bootstrap/bootstrap.sh\n"
msgstr "https://<example.com>/pub/bootstrap/bootstrap.sh\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:22
msgid ""
"Do not disable SSL in your bootstrap script.  Ensure that [guimenu]``Enable "
"SSL`` is checked in the {webui}, or that the setting `USING_SSL=1` exists in "
"the bootstrap script.  If you disable SSL, the registration process requires "
"custom SSL certificates.  For more about custom certificates, see "
"xref:administration:ssl-certs.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"No desactiveu l'SSL a l'script bootstrap.  Assegureu-vos que [guimenu]."
"Activa SSL. estigui marcat a la {webui}, o que la configuració .USINGSSL11. "
"existeixi a l'script d'arrencada.  Si desactives l'SSL, el procés de "
"registre requereix certificats SSL personalitzats.  Per obtenir més "
"informació sobre els certificats personalitzats, vegeu xref:administration"
":ssl-certs.adoc[]."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:23
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:47
msgid ""
"To register and use {centos}{nbsp}6, {oracle}{nbsp}6, {rhel}{nbsp}6, or "
"{sleses}{nbsp}6 clients, you need to configure the {productname} Server to "
"support older types of SSL encryption.  For more information about how to "
"resolve this error, see ``Registering Older Clients`` at "
"xref:client-configuration:tshoot-clients.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per registrar i utilitzar {centos}{nbsp}6, {oracle}{nbsp}6, {rhel}{nbsp}6, o "
"{sleses}{nbsp}6 clients, heu de configurar el servidor {productname} per "
"admetre tipus antics d'encriptació SSL.  Per a més informació sobre com "
"resoldre aquest error, vegeu ].Registering Older Clients at a xref:client-"
"configuration:tshoot-clients.adoc[]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "Editing a Bootstrap Script"
msgstr "Edició d'un script Bootstrap"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:25
msgid ""
"You can copy and modify the template bootstrap script you created to "
"customize it.  A minimal requirement when modifying a bootstrap script for "
"use with {productname} is the inclusion of an activation key.  Most packages "
"are signed with GPG, so you also need to have trusted GPG keys on your "
"system to install them."
msgstr ""
"Podeu copiar i modificar l'script d'arrencada de la plantilla que heu creat "
"per personalitzar-lo.  Un requisit mínim quan es modifica un script "
"d'arrencada per utilitzar-lo amb {productname} és la inclusió d'una clau "
"d'activació.  La majoria dels paquets estan signats amb GPG, de manera que "
"també heu de tenir claus GPG de confiança al vostre sistema per instal·lar-"
"les."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:26
msgid ""
"In this procedure, you need to know the exact name of your activation keys.  "
"Navigate to menu:Home[Overview] and, in the [guimenu]``Tasks`` box, click "
"[guimenu]``Manage Activation Keys``.  All keys created for channels are "
"listed on this page.  You must enter the full name of the key you wish to "
"use in the bootstrap script exactly as presented in the key field.  For more "
"information about activation keys, see "
"xref:client-configuration:activation-keys.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"En aquest procediment, heu de conèixer el nom exacte de les vostres claus "
"d'activació.  Navega al menú:Inici[Vista general] i, al quadre [guimenu]."
"Tasques., feu clic a [guimenu].Gestioneu les tecles d'activació..  Totes les "
"claus creades per als canals es llisten en aquesta pàgina.  Heu d'introduir "
"el nom complet de la clau que voleu utilitzar a l'script bootstrap "
"exactament com es presenta al camp clau.  Per obtenir més informació sobre "
"les claus d'activació, vegeu xref:client-configuration:activation-keys."
"adoc[]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Modifying a Bootstrap Script"
msgstr "Procediment: Modificació d'un script Bootstrap"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:28
msgid ""
"On your {productname} server, as root at the command line change to the "
"bootstrap directory with:"
msgstr ""
"Al vostre servidor {productname}, com a root a la línia d'ordres, canvieu al "
"directori bootstrap amb:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:29
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "cd /srv/www/htdocs/pub/bootstrap/\n"
msgstr "cd /srv/www/htdocs/pub/bootstrap/\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:30
msgid ""
"Create and rename two copies of the template bootstrap script for use with "
"each of your clients."
msgstr ""
"Creeu i reanomeneu dues còpies de l'script bootstrap de la plantilla per "
"utilitzar-lo amb cadascun dels vostres clients."

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:31
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cp bootstrap.sh bootstrap-sles12.sh\n"
"cp bootstrap.sh bootstrap-sles15.sh\n"
msgstr ""
"cp bootstrap.sh bootstrap-sles12.sh\n"
"cp bootstrap.sh bootstrap-sles15.sh\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:32
msgid "Open [path]``bootstrap-sles15.sh`` for modification."
msgstr "Obriu [path].bootstrap-sles15.sh. per a la modificació."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:33
msgid ""
"Scroll down until you can see the text shown below.  If ``exit 1`` exists in "
"the file, comment it out by typing a hash or pound sign (&#35;) at the "
"beginning of the line.  This activates the script.  Enter the name of the "
"key for this script in the ``ACTIVATION_KEYS=`` field:"
msgstr ""
"Desplaceu-vos cap avall fins que veieu el text que es mostra a continuació.  "
"Si .exit 1. existeix en el fitxer, comenteu-ho escrivint un signe de hash o "
"lliura (3535;) al començament de la línia.  Això activa l'script.  Introduïu "
"el nom de la clau per a aquest script al camp  theACTIVATIONKEYS::"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:34
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"echo \"Enable this script: comment (with #'s) this block (or, at least "
"just\"\n"
"echo \"the exit below)\"\n"
"echo\n"
"#exit 1\n"
msgstr ""
"echo \"Enable this script: comment (with )'s) this block (or, almenys just\" "
"echo \"the exit BELOW) echo\n"
" exit 1\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:35
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# can be edited, but probably correct (unless created during initial "
"install):\n"
"# NOTE: ACTIVATION_KEYS *must* be used to bootstrap a client machine.\n"
"ACTIVATION_KEYS=1-sles15\n"
"ORG_GPG_KEY=\n"
msgstr ""
"): es pot editar, però probablement corregir (tret que es creï durant la "
"instal·lació inicial):\n"
". NOTA: ACTIVATIONKEYS *ha d'usar-se per arrencar una màquina client.\n"
"ACTIVATIONKEYS1-1-sles15\n"
"ORGGPGKEY=\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:36
msgid ""
"When you have finished, save the file, and repeat this procedure for the "
"second bootstrap script."
msgstr ""
"Quan hàgiu acabat, deseu el fitxer i repetiu aquest procediment per al segon "
"script d'arrencada."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:37
msgid ""
"By default, bootstrap script will try to install "
"[package]``venv-salt-minion`` for Salt clients if it's available in the "
"bootstrap repository and [package]``salt-minion`` if there is no Salt bundle "
"in the bootstrap repository.  It is posible to avoid installing Salt bundle "
"and keep using [package]``salt-minion`` if you need it for some reason. See "
"xref:client-configuration:contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc[Salt Bundle] for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"De manera predeterminada, l'script bootstrap intentarà instal·lar [package"
"].venv-salt-minion. per als clients Salt si està disponible al repositori "
"bootstrap i [package].salt-minion. si no hi ha cap paquet Salt al repositori "
"bootstrap.  És possible evitar instal·lar el fardell de sal i seguir "
"utilitzant [package].salt-minion. si el necessiteu per algun motiu. Vegeu "
"xref:client-configuration:contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc[Salt Bundle] per "
"als detalls."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "Connect Clients"
msgstr "Connecta els clients"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:39
msgid ""
"When you have finished creating your script, you can use it to register "
"clients."
msgstr ""
"Quan hàgiu acabat de crear el vostre script, el podreu utilitzar per "
"registrar clients."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Running the Bootstrap Script"
msgstr "Procediment: Executar l'script Bootstrap"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:41
msgid "On the {productname} Server, log in as root."
msgstr "Al servidor {productname}, inicieu sessió com a root."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:42
msgid "At the command prompt, and change to the bootstrap directory:"
msgstr "A l'indicador d'ordres i canvieu al directori d'arrencada:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:44
msgid ""
"Run this command to execute the bootstrap script on the client; replace "
"[systemitem]`` EXAMPLE.COM`` with the host name of your client:"
msgstr ""
"Executeu aquesta ordre per a executar l'script bootstrap al client; "
"reemplaceu [systemitem] EXAMPLE EXAMPLE.COM the amb el nom de l'amfitrió del "
"vostre client:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "cat bootstrap-sles15.sh | ssh root@EXAMPLE.COM /bin/bash\n"
msgstr "cat bootstrap-sles15.sh   ssh root.EXEMPLE.COM /bin/bash\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:46
msgid "Alternatively, on the client, run this command:"
msgstr "Alternativament, en el client, executeu aquesta ordre:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:47
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"curl -Sks https://server_hostname/pub/bootstrap/bootstrap-sles15.sh | "
"/bin/bash\n"
msgstr ""
"curl -Sks https://serverhostname/pub/bootstrap/bootstrap-sles15.sh   /bin/"
"bash\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:48
msgid ""
"To avoid problems, make sure the bootstrap script is executed using "
"[command]``bash``."
msgstr ""
"Per evitar problemes, assegureu-vos que l'script bootstrap s'executa "
"utilitzant [command].bash.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:49
msgid ""
"This script downloads the required dependencies located in the repositories "
"directory you created earlier."
msgstr ""
"Aquest script baixa les dependències necessàries ubicades al directori de "
"repositoris que heu creat anteriorment."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:50
msgid ""
"When the script has finished running, you can check that your client is "
"registered correctly by opening the {productname} {webui} and navigating to "
"menu:Systems[Overview] to ensure the new client is listed."
msgstr ""
"Quan l'script hagi acabat d'executar-se, podeu comprovar que el vostre "
"client s'ha registrat correctament obrint el {productname} {webui} i "
"navegant al menú:Systems[Overview] per assegurar-vos que el nou client està "
"llistat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:51
msgid ""
"If you used the script to register the Salt client, open the {productname} "
"{webui} and navigate to menu:Salt[Keys] to accept the client key."
msgstr ""
"Si heu utilitzat l'script per registrar el client Salt, obriu el "
"{productname} {webui} i navegueu al menú:Salt[Keys] per acceptar la clau del "
"client."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-bootstrap.adoc:52
msgid ""
"When new packages or updates are installed on the client using "
"{productname}, any end user license agreements (EULAs) are automatically "
"accepted.  To review a package EULA, open the package detail page in the "
"{webui}."
msgstr ""
"Quan s'instal·len nous paquets o actualitzacions al client utilitzant "
"{productname}, s'accepten automàticament qualsevol acord de llicència "
"d'usuari final (EULAs).  Per revisar un paquet EULA, obriu la pàgina de "
"detalls del paquet a la {webui}."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "Manual Salt client registration"
msgstr "Registre manual del client Salt"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:3
msgid ""
"In most cases, Salt clients are registered accurately with the default "
"bootstrap methods.  However, you can use Salt to register the client to the "
"{productname} Server manually by editing the Salt minion file on the client, "
"and providing the fully qualified domain name (FQDN) of the server.  This "
"method uses ports 4505 and 4506 inbound to the server.  This method requires "
"no configuration on the {productname} Server aside from ensuring that these "
"ports are open."
msgstr ""
"En la majoria dels casos, els clients de Salt es registren amb precisió amb "
"els mètodes d'arrencada per defecte.  No obstant això, podeu utilitzar Salt "
"per registrar el client al servidor {productname} manualment editant el "
"fitxer de minions Salt al client i proporcionant el nom de domini (FQDN) "
"completament qualificat del servidor.  Aquest mètode utilitza els ports 4505 "
"i 4506 entrants al servidor.  Aquest mètode no requereix cap configuració al "
"servidor {productname} a part d'assegurar que aquests ports estan oberts."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:4
msgid ""
"Registering on the command line is also possible with traditional clients, "
"but it requires more steps.  It is not covered here.  Use the bootstrap "
"script procedure to register traditional clients.  For more information, see "
"xref:registration-bootstrap.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Registrar-se a la línia de comandes també és possible amb clients "
"tradicionals, però requereix més passos.  No està cobert aquí.  Utilitzeu el "
"procediment de script bootstrap per registrar clients tradicionals.  Per a "
"més informació, vegeu xref:registration-bootstrap.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:5
msgid ""
"This procedure requires that you have installed the "
"[package]``venv-salt-minion`` (Salt bundle) or the [package]``salt-minion`` "
"package on the Salt client before registration.  Both use configuration "
"files in different locations and filenames remain the same.  The systemd "
"service filename is different."
msgstr ""
"Aquest procediment requereix que hàgiu instal·lat el paquet [package].venv-"
"salt-minion. (paquet de sal) o el paquet [package].salt-minion. al client de "
"Salt abans de registrar-vos.  Tots dos utilitzen fitxers de configuració en "
"diferents ubicacions i els noms de fitxer continuen sent els mateixos.  El "
"nom de fitxer del servei «systemd» és diferent."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:6
msgid ""
"Bootstrapping this way will only work if you use the "
"[package]``salt-minion`` being part of the client tools channels or of an "
"official {suse} distributions."
msgstr ""
"Bootstrapping d'aquesta manera només funcionarà si utilitzeu el [package"
"].salt-minion. formant part dels canals d'eines del client o d'una "
"distribució oficial {suse}."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Salt Bundle configuration"
msgstr "Configuració de Salt Bundle"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Salt Bundle ([package]``venv-salt-minion``)"
msgstr "Salt Bundle ([package])venv-salt-minion))"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:9
msgid "[path]``/etc/venv-salt-minion/``"
msgstr "[camí]//etc/venv-salt-minion//"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:10
msgid "[path]``/etc/venv-salt-minion/minion``"
msgstr "[camí]``/etc/venv-salt-minion/minion``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:11
msgid "[path]``/etc/venv-salt-minion/minion.d/NAME.conf``"
msgstr "[camí]//etc/venv-salt-minion/minion.d/NAME.conf."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:12
msgid "systemd service file: [path]``venv-salt-minion.service``"
msgstr "fitxer de servei systemd: [path]:venv-salt-minion.service``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:13
msgid ""
"For more information about the Salt bundle, see "
"xref:client-configuration:contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc[Salt Bundle]."
msgstr ""
"Per a més informació sobre el fibrat de sal, vegeu xref:client-configuration"
":contact-methods-saltbundle.adoc[Salt Bundle]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Registering Clients with Salt Bundle Configuration File"
msgstr ""
"Procediment: Registre de clients amb el fitxer de configuració Salt Bundle"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:15
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:34
msgid ""
"On the Salt client, open the [literal]``minion`` configuration file.  The "
"configuration file is either located at:"
msgstr ""
"Al client Salt, obriu el fitxer de configuració [literal].minion..  El "
"fitxer de configuració es troba a:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/venv-salt-minion/minion\n"
msgstr "/etc/venv-salt-minion/minion\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/venv-salt-minion/minion.d/NAME.conf\n"
msgstr "/etc/venv-salt-minion/minion.d/NAME.conf\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:19
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:38
msgid ""
"In the file add or edit the FQDN of the {productname} Server or Proxy, and "
"the activation key if any. Also add the other configuration parameters "
"listed below."
msgstr ""
"Al fitxer afegiu o editeu la FQDN del servidor o servidor intermediari "
"{productname} i la clau d'activació si n'hi ha. Afegiu també els altres "
"paràmetres de configuració llistats a continuació."

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:20
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "master: SERVER.EXAMPLE.COM\n"
msgstr "master: SERVER.EXAMPLE.COM\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:21
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:40
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"grains:\n"
"  susemanager:\n"
