#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "System Groups"
msgstr "Grups de sistema"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:2
msgid ""
"You can use system groups to make it easier to manage a large number of "
"clients.  Groups can be used to perform bulk actions on clients such as "
"applying updates, configuration channels, salt states, or formulas."
msgstr ""
"Podeu utilitzar grups del sistema per facilitar la gestió d'un gran nombre "
"de clients.  Els grups es poden utilitzar per realitzar accions massives en "
"clients com ara aplicar actualitzacions, canals de configuració, estats de "
"sal o fórmules."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:3
msgid ""
"You can organize clients into groups in any way that works for your "
"environment.  For example, you could organize clients on which operating "
"system is installed, which physical location they are in, or the type of "
"workload they are handling.  Clients can be in any number of groups, so you "
"can define your groups in different ways."
msgstr ""
"Pots organitzar clients en grups de qualsevol manera que funcioni per al teu "
"entorn.  Per exemple, es podrien organitzar clients en quin sistema operatiu "
"està instal·lat, en quina ubicació física es troben o el tipus de càrrega de "
"treball que estan manejant.  Els clients poden estar en qualsevol nombre de "
"grups, de manera que podeu definir els vostres grups de diferents maneres."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:4
msgid ""
"When you have clients organized into groups, you can perform updates on all "
"clients in one or more groups, or on intersections between groups.  For "
"example, you can define one group for all Salt clients, and another group "
"for all SLES clients.  You can then perform updates on all Salt clients, or "
"use the intersection between the groups, and update all Salt SLES clients."
msgstr ""
"Quan teniu clients organitzats en grups, podeu fer actualitzacions de tots "
"els clients en un o més grups, o en interseccions entre grups.  Per exemple, "
"podeu definir un grup per a tots els clients de Salt, i un altre grup per a "
"tots els clients de SLES.  A continuació, podeu realitzar actualitzacions a "
"tots els clients de Salt, o utilitzar la intersecció entre els grups, i "
"actualitzar tots els clients de Salt SLES."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create Groups"
msgstr "Crea grups"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:6
msgid ""
"You need to create some groups before you can use them to organize your "
"clients."
msgstr ""
"Heu de crear alguns grups abans de poder utilitzar-los per organitzar els "
"vostres clients."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Creating a New System Group"
msgstr "Procediment: Creació d'un nou grup de sistema"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:8
msgid "In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[System Groups]."
msgstr "A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Systems Groups]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:10
msgid "Give your new group a name and a description."
msgstr "Doneu al vostre nou grup un nom i una descripció."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:11
msgid "Click btn:[Create Group] to save your group."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Crea un grup] per a desar el grup."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:12
msgid "Repeat for each group you require."
msgstr "Repeteix per a cada grup que necessitis."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Add Clients to Groups"
msgstr "Afegeix clients a grups"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:14
msgid ""
"You can add individual clients to your groups, or add multiple clients at "
"the same time."
msgstr ""
"Podeu afegir clients individuals als vostres grups, o afegir diversos "
"clients al mateix temps."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Adding A Single Client to a Group"
msgstr "Procediment: Afegir un client únic a un grup"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:16
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[System List] and "
"click the name of the client to add."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Llista de sistemes] i feu "
"clic al nom del client per afegir-lo."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:17
msgid "Navigate to the menu:Groups[Join] tab."
msgstr "Navega a la pestanya menú:Grups[Uneix]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:18
msgid "Check the group to join and click btn:[Join Selected Groups]."
msgstr ""
"Marqueu el grup per unir-vos i feu clic a btn:[Uneix els grups seleccionats]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Adding Multiple Clients to a Group"
msgstr "Procediment: Afegir múltiples clients a un grup"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:20
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[System Groups] and "
"click the name of the group to add clients to."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[System Groups] i feu clic "
"al nom del grup per afegir clients."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:21
msgid "Navigate to the [guimenu]``Target systems`` tab."
msgstr "Navega a la pestanya [guimenu].Target systems.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:22
msgid "Check the clients to add and click btn:[Add Systems]."
msgstr "Consulta els clients per afegir i fer clic a btn:[Afegeix sistemes]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Adding Multiple Clients to a Group with SSM"
msgstr "Procediment: Afegir múltiples clients a un grup amb SSM"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:24
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[System List] and "
"check each client to add, this adds the clients to the system set manager."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Llista de sistemes] i "
"comproveu cada client per afegir, això afegeix els clients al gestor de "
"conjunts del sistema."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:25
msgid ""
"Navigate to menu:Systems[System Set Manager], and go to the "
"[guimenu]``Groups`` tab."
msgstr ""
"Navega al menú:Sistemes[Gestor de conjunts del sistema], i ves a la pestanya "
"[guimenu].Grups.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:26
msgid "Locate the group to join and check [guimenu]``Add``."
msgstr "Localitzeu el grup per a unir-vos i marqueu [guimenu].Afegeix.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:27
msgid "Click btn:[Alter Membership]."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Alterar la pertinença]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:28
msgid "Click btn:[Confirm] to join the clients to the selected group."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Confirm] per unir-vos als clients al grup seleccionat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:29
msgid ""
"For more information about the system set manager, see "
"xref:client-configuration:system-set-manager.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per obtenir més informació sobre el gestor de conjunts de sistemes, vegeu "
"xref:client-configuration:system-set-manager.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:30
msgid ""
"You can see which clients are in a group by navigating to "
"menu:Systems[System Groups], clicking the name of the group, and navigating "
"to the [guimenu]``Systems`` tab.  Alternatively, you can see a graphical "
"representation of your system groups by navigating to "
"menu:Systems[Visualization > Systems Grouping]."
msgstr ""
"Podeu veure quins clients estan en un grup navegant al menú:Sistemes[Grups "
"del sistema], fent clic al nom del grup i navegant a la pestanya [guimenu]."
"Sistemes..  Alternativament, podeu veure una representació gràfica dels "
"grups del vostre sistema navegant al menú:Sistemes[Visualització ]. "
"Agrupament de sistemes]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "Work with Groups"
msgstr "Treballa amb grups"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:32
msgid ""
"When you have your clients arranged into groups, you can use your groups to "
"manage updates.  For Salt clients, you can also apply states and formulas to "
"all clients in a group."
msgstr ""
"Quan tinguis els teus clients organitzats en grups, pots utilitzar els teus "
"grups per gestionar actualitzacions.  Per als clients de Salt, també podeu "
"aplicar estats i fórmules a tots els clients d'un grup."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:33
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[System Groups].  The "
"list shows an icon if there are updates available for any of the clients in "
"the group.  Click the icon to see more information about the updates "
"available and to apply them to the clients."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Systems Groups].  La "
"llista mostra una icona si hi ha actualitzacions disponibles per a qualsevol "
"dels clients del grup.  Feu clic a la icona per veure més informació sobre "
"les actualitzacions disponibles i per aplicar-les als clients."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:34
msgid ""
"You can also work with more than one group at a time.  Select the groups you "
"want to work with, and click btn:[Work with union] to select every client in "
"every selected group."
msgstr ""
"També es pot treballar amb més d'un grup a la vegada.  Seleccioneu els grups "
"amb els quals voleu treballar i feu clic a btn:[Treballa amb la unió] per a "
"seleccionar cada client de cada grup seleccionat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-groups.adoc:35
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can work on intersections of groups.  Select two or more "
"groups, and click btn:[Work with intersection] to select only those clients "
"that exist in all the selected groups.  For example, you might have one "
"group for all Salt clients, and another group for all SLES clients.  The "
"intersection of these groups would be all Salt SLES clients."
msgstr ""
"Alternativament, podeu treballar en interseccions de grups.  Seleccioneu dos "
"o més grups, i feu clic a btn:[Treballa amb intersecció] per a seleccionar "
"només aquells clients que existeixen en tots els grups seleccionats.  Per "
"exemple, podeu tenir un grup per a tots els clients de Salt, i un altre grup "
"per a tots els clients de SLES.  La intersecció d'aquests grups serien tots "
"els clients de Salt SLES."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "System Locking"
msgstr "Bloqueig del sistema"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:2
msgid ""
"System locks are used to prevent actions from occurring on a client.  For "
"example, a system lock prevents a client from being updated or restarted.  "
"This is useful for clients running production software, or to prevent "
"accidental changes.  You can disable the system lock when you are ready to "
"perform actions."
msgstr ""
"Els bloqueigs del sistema s'utilitzen per evitar que es produeixin accions "
"en un client.  Per exemple, un bloqueig del sistema impedeix que un client "
"s'actualitzi o es reiniciï.  Això és útil per als clients que executen "
"programari de producció, o per evitar canvis accidentals.  Podeu desactivar "
"el bloqueig del sistema quan estigueu preparat per a realitzar accions."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:3
msgid "System locks are implemented differently on traditional and Salt clients."
msgstr ""
"Els panys del sistema s'implementen de manera diferent en els clients "
"tradicionals i de Salt."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:4
#, no-wrap
msgid "System Locks on Traditional Clients"
msgstr "Bloqueig del sistema als clients tradicionals"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:5
msgid ""
"When a traditional client is locked, no actions can be scheduled using the "
"{webui}, and a padlock icon is displayed next to the name of the client in "
"the menu:System[System List]."
msgstr ""
"Quan un client tradicional està bloquejat, no es poden programar accions "
"utilitzant el {webui}, i es mostra una icona de cadenat al costat del nom "
"del client al menú:System[Llista de sistema]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: System Locking a Traditional Client"
msgstr "Procediment: bloqueig del sistema a un client tradicional"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:7
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:15
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to the [guimenu]``System Details`` "
"page for the client you want to lock."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu a la pàgina [guimenu].Detalls del sistema. "
"per al client que voleu bloquejar."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:8
msgid "Under [guimenu]``Lock Status``, click btn:[Lock this system]."
msgstr ""
"A [guimenu]].Bloqueja l'estat]., feu clic a btn:[Bloqueja aquest sistema]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:9
msgid "The client remains locked until you click btn:[Unlock this system]."
msgstr ""
"El client roman bloquejat fins que feu clic a btn:[Desbloqueja aquest "
"sistema]."

#. Something about requiring admin rights here maybe? --LKB 20200514
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Some actions can still be completed on locked traditional clients, including "
"remote commands, and automated patch updates.  To stop automated patch "
"updates, navigate to the [guimenu]``System Details`` page for the client, "
"and on the [guimenu]``Properties`` tab, uncheck [guimenu]``Auto Patch "
"Update``."
msgstr ""
"Algunes accions encara es poden completar en clients tradicionals "
"bloquejats, incloses ordres remotes i actualitzacions de pedaç "
"automatitzades.  Per aturar les actualitzacions de pedaç automatitzades, "
"navegueu a la pàgina [guimenu].Detalls del sistema. per al client, i a la "
"pestanya [guimenu].Propietats., desmarqueu [guimenu].Actualització "
"automàtica del pedaço``."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "System Locks on Salt Clients"
msgstr "Bloquejos del sistema als clients de Salt"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:12
msgid ""
"When a Salt client is locked, or put into blackout mode, no actions can be "
"scheduled, Salt execution commands are disabled, and a yellow banner is "
"displayed on the [guimenu]``System Details`` page.  In this mode, actions "
"can be scheduled for the locked client using the {webui} or the API, but the "
"actions fail."
msgstr ""
"Quan un client Salt està bloquejat o posat en mode d'apagada, no es poden "
"programar accions, les ordres d'execució de Salt estan desactivades i es "
"mostra un bàner groc a la pàgina [guimenu].Detalls del sistema..  En aquest "
"mode, es poden programar accions per al client bloquejat utilitzant el "
"{webui} o l'API, però les accions fallen."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:13
msgid "The locking mechanism is not available for Salt SSH clients."
msgstr ""
"El mecanisme de bloqueig no està disponible per als clients de Salt SSH."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: System Locking a Salt Client"
msgstr "Procediment: Sistema de bloqueig d'un client de sal"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:16
msgid ""
"Navigate to the [guimenu]``Formulas`` tab, check the system lock formula, "
"and click btn:[Save]."
msgstr ""
"Navegueu a la pestanya [guimenu]].Formulas]., marqueu la fórmula de bloqueig "
"del sistema i feu clic a btn:[Desa]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:17
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:Formulas[System Lock] tab, check [guimenu]``Lock "
"system``, and click btn:[Save]."
msgstr ""
"Navega a la pestanya menú:Formulas[Bloqueig del sistema], marca [guimenu]]."
"Bloqueja el sistema]. i fes clic a btn:[Desa]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:18
msgid ""
"On this page, you can also enable specific Salt modules while the client is "
"locked."
msgstr ""
"En aquesta pàgina, també podeu habilitar mòduls específics de Salt mentre el "
"client està bloquejat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:19
msgid "When you have made your changes, you might need to apply the highstate."
msgstr "Quan hàgiu fet els canvis, és possible que hàgiu d'aplicar l'estat alt."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:20
msgid ""
"In this case, a banner in the {webui} notifies you.  The client remains "
"locked until you remove the system lock formula."
msgstr ""
"En aquest cas, un bàner de la {webui} us notifica.  El client roman "
"bloquejat fins que elimineu la fórmula de bloqueig del sistema."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:21
msgid ""
"For more information about blackout mode in Salt, see "
"https://docs.saltstack.com/en/latest/topics/blackout/index.html."
msgstr ""
"Per a més informació sobre el mode d'apagada a Salt, vegeu https://docs."
"saltstack.com/ca/latest/topics/blackout/index.html."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Package Locks"
msgstr "Bloquejos de paquets"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:23
msgid ""
"Package locking can be used on several clients, but different feature sets "
"are available.  You must differentiate between:"
msgstr ""
"El bloqueig de paquets es pot utilitzar en diversos clients, però hi ha "
"disponibles diferents conjunts de característiques.  Heu de diferenciar "
"entre:"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:24
msgid "{sle} and {opensuse} (zypp-based) versus {rhel} or {debian} clients, and"
msgstr "{sle} i {opensuse} (basat en zpp) versus {rhel} o {debian} clients, i"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:25
msgid "Traditional versus Salt clients."
msgstr "Clients tradicionals versus Salt."

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Package Locks on Zypp-based Systems"
msgstr "Bloquejos de paquets en sistemes basats en Zypp"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:27
msgid ""
"Systems with the Zypper package manager have package locking available on "
"traditional and Salt clients."
msgstr ""
"Els sistemes amb el gestor de paquets Zypper disposen de tancament de "
"paquets disponibles en clients tradicionals i Salt."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:28
msgid ""
"Package locks are used to prevent unauthorized installation or upgrades to "
"software packages.  When a package has been locked, it shows a padlock icon, "
"indicating that it cannot be installed.  Any attempt to install a locked "
"package is reported as an error in the event log."
msgstr ""
"Els bloquejos de paquets s'utilitzen per evitar la instal·lació no "
"autoritzada o les actualitzacions als paquets de programari.  Quan un paquet "
"ha estat bloquejat, mostra una icona de cadenat, indicant que no es pot "
"instal·lar.  Qualsevol intent d'instal·lar un paquet bloquejat s'informa com "
"un error en el registre d'esdeveniments."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:29
msgid ""
"Locked packages cannot be installed, upgraded, or removed, neither through "
"the {productname} {webui}, nor directly on the client machine using a "
"package manager.  Locked packages also indirectly lock any dependent "
"packages."
msgstr ""
"Els paquets bloquejats no es poden instal·lar, actualitzar o eliminar, ni a "
"través de {productname} {webui}, ni directament a la màquina client que "
"utilitza un gestor de paquets.  Els paquets bloquejats també bloquegen "
"indirectament qualsevol paquet dependent."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:30
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Using Package Locks"
msgstr "Procediment: Ús de blocatges de paquets"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:31
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:40
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:Software[Packages > Lock] tab on the managed system to "
"see a list of all available packages."
msgstr ""
"Navega a la pestanya menu:Software[Packages . Lock] del sistema gestionat "
"per a veure una llista de tots els paquets disponibles."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:32
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:41
msgid ""
"Select the packages to lock, and click btn:[Request Lock].  Pick date and "
"time for the lock to activate.  By default, the lock is activated as soon as "
"possible.  Note that the lock might not activate immediately."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu els paquets a bloquejar i feu clic a btn:[Sol·licitud de "
"bloqueig].  Trieu la data i l'hora per activar el bloqueig.  Per defecte, el "
"bloqueig s'activa tan aviat com sigui possible.  Tingueu en compte que el "
"bloqueig pot no activar-se immediatament."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:33
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:42
msgid ""
"To remove a package lock, select the packages to unlock and click "
"btn:[Request Unlock].  Pick date and time as with activating the lock."
msgstr ""
"Per a eliminar un blocatge de paquets, seleccioneu els paquets a "
"desbloquejar i feu clic a btn:[Desbloquejar la sol·licitud].  Trieu la data "
"i l'hora com amb l'activació del bloqueig."

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Package Locks on {rhel}- and {debian}-like Systems"
msgstr "Paquets bloquejats en sistemes {rhel}- i {debian}-like"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:35
msgid ""
"Some {rhel}- and {debian}-like systems have package locking available on "
"Salt clients."
msgstr ""
"Alguns sistemes semblants a {rhel}- i {debian} tenen el bloqueig de paquets "
"disponible en clients de Salt."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:36
msgid ""
"On {rhel}- and {debian}-like systems, package locks are only used to prevent "
"unauthorized upgrades or removals to software packages.  When a package has "
"been locked, it shows a padlock icon, indicating that it cannot be changed.  "
"Any attempt to change a locked package is reported as an error in the event "
"log."
msgstr ""
"En sistemes semblants a {rhel}- i {debian}, els blocatges de paquets només "
"s'utilitzen per evitar actualitzacions o eliminacions no autoritzades a "
"paquets de programari.  Quan un paquet ha estat bloquejat, mostra una icona "
"de cadenat, indicant que no es pot canviar.  Qualsevol intent de canviar un "
"paquet bloquejat s'informa com un error en el registre d'esdeveniments."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:37
msgid ""
"Locked packages cannot be upgraded or removed, neither through the "
"{productname} {webui}, nor directly on the client machine using a package "
"manager.  Locked packages also indirectly lock any dependent packages."
msgstr ""
"Els paquets bloquejats no es poden actualitzar ni eliminar, ni a través del "
"{productname} {webui}, ni directament a la màquina client que utilitza un "
"gestor de paquets.  Els paquets bloquejats també bloquegen indirectament "
"qualsevol paquet dependent."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-locking.adoc:39
msgid ""
"On the {rhel} 7 systems, install the [package]``yum-plugin-versionlock`` "
"package as [systemitem]``root``.  On the {rhel} 8 systems, install the "
"[package]``python3-dnf-plugin-versionlock`` package as "
"[systemitem]``root``.  On {debian} systems, the ``apt`` tool has the locking "
"feature included."
msgstr ""
"En els sistemes {rhel} 7, instal·leu el paquet [package].yum-plugin-"
"versionlock. com a [systemitem].root..  En els {rhel} 8 sistemes, instal·leu "
"el paquet [package].python3-dnf-plugin-versionlock. com a [systemitem]."
"root..  En els sistemes {debian}, l'eina .apt. té inclosa la característica "
"de bloqueig."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-set-manager.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "System Set Manager"
msgstr "Gestor de conjunts de sistema"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-set-manager.adoc:2
msgid ""
"The system set manager (SSM) is used to perform actions on more than one "
"client at a time.  SSM creates ephemeral sets of clients, making it useful "
"for one-off actions that you need to apply to a number of clients.  If you "
"want more permanent sets, consider using system groups instead.  For more "
"information about system groups, see "
"xref:client-configuration:system-groups.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"El gestor de conjunts de sistema (SSM) s'utilitza per realitzar accions en "
"més d'un client alhora.  L'SSM crea conjunts efímers de clients, fent-lo "
"útil per a accions puntuals que necessiteu aplicar a diversos clients.  Si "
"voleu conjunts més permanents, considereu utilitzar grups de sistema en el "
"seu lloc.  Per a més informació sobre els grups de sistema, vegeu xref"
":client-configuration:system-groups.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-set-manager.adoc:3
msgid ""
"The actions available for use in SSM are listed in this table.  The icons in "
"this table indicate:"
msgstr ""
"Les accions disponibles per al seu ús en SSM es llisten en aquesta taula.  "
