msgstr "mgr-create-bootstrap-repo --create SLE-12-SP2-x8664 --force\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:50
msgid ""
"If you do not want to create bootstrap repositories manually, you can check "
"whether LTSS is available for the product and bootstrap repository you need."
msgstr ""
"Si no voleu crear repositoris bootstrap manualment, podeu comprovar si LTSS "
"està disponible per al repositori de producte i bootstrap que necessiteu."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "Cloned Salt Clients"
msgstr "Clients de sal clonada"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:52
msgid ""
"If you have used your hypervisor clone utility, and attempted to register "
"the cloned Salt client, you might get this error:"
msgstr ""
"Si heu utilitzat la vostra utilitat de clon de l'hipervisor i heu intentat "
"registrar el client de Salt clonat, és possible que obtingueu aquest error:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "We're sorry, but the system could not be found.\n"
msgstr "Ho sentim, però no s'ha pogut trobar el sistema.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:54
msgid ""
"This is caused by the new, cloned, system having the same machine ID as an "
"existing, registered, system.  You can adjust this manually to correct the "
"error and register the cloned system successfully."
msgstr ""
"Això és causat pel nou sistema, clonat, que té el mateix ID de màquina que "
"un sistema existent, registrat.  Podeu ajustar-ho manualment per a corregir "
"l'error i registrar el sistema clonat amb èxit."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:55
msgid ""
"For more information and instructions, see "
"xref:administration:tshoot-registerclones.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per a més informació i instruccions, vegeu xref:administration:tshoot-"
"registerclones.adoc[]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "Disabling the FQDNS grain"
msgstr "Desactivar el gra FQDNS"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:57
msgid ""
"The FQDNS grain returns the list of all the fully qualified DNS services in "
"the system.  Collecting this information is usually a fast process, but if "
"the DNS settings have been misconfigured, it could take a much longer time.  "
"In some cases, the client could become unresponsive, or crash."
msgstr ""
"El gra FQDNS retorna la llista de tots els serveis DNS completament "
"qualificats del sistema.  Recopilar aquesta informació sol ser un procés "
"ràpid, però si la configuració del DNS s'ha configurat malament, podria "
"trigar molt més temps.  En alguns casos, el client podria quedar-se sense "
"resposta, o caure."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:58
msgid ""
"To prevent this problem, you can disable the FQDNS grain with a Salt flag.  "
"If you disable the grain, you can use a network module to provide FQDNS "
"services, without the risk of the client becoming unresponsive."
msgstr ""
"Per evitar aquest problema, podeu desactivar el gra FQDNS amb una bandera de "
"sal.  Si desactives el gra, pots utilitzar un mòdul de xarxa per "
"proporcionar serveis de FQDNS, sense el risc que el client es converteixi en "
"impensable."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:59
msgid ""
"This only applies to older Salt clients.  If you registered your Salt client "
"recently, the FQDNS grain is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Això només s'aplica als clients més antics de Salt.  Si heu registrat el "
"vostre client Salt recentment, el gra FQDNS està desactivat per defecte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:60
msgid ""
"On the {productname} Server, at the command prompt, use this command to "
"disable the FQDNS grain:"
msgstr ""
"Al servidor {productname}, a l'indicador d'ordres, utilitzeu aquesta ordre "
"per a desactivar el gra FQDNS:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:61
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt '*' state.sls util.mgr_disable_fqdns_grain\n"
msgstr "estat «*» de la sal.sls util.mgrdisablefqdnsgrain\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:62
msgid ""
"This command restarts each client and generate Salt events that the server "
"needs to process.  If you have a large number of clients, you can execute "
"the command in batch mode instead:"
msgstr ""
"Aquesta ordre reinicia cada client i genera esdeveniments Salt que el "
"servidor necessita processar.  Si teniu un gran nombre de clients, podeu "
"executar l'ordre en mode per lots:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt --batch-size 50 '*' state.sls util.mgr_disable_fqdns_grain\n"
msgstr "salt --batch-size 50 '*' estat.sls util.mgrdisablefqdnsgrain\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:64
msgid ""
"Wait for the batch command to finish executing.  Do not interrupt the "
"process with kbd:[Ctrl+C]."
msgstr ""
"Espereu que l'ordre per lots acabi d'executar-se.  No interrompeu el procés "
"amb kbd:[Ctrl+C]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mounting /tmp with noexec"
msgstr "Muntant /tmp amb noexec"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:66
msgid ""
"Salt runs remote commands from [filename]``/tmp`` on the client's file "
"system.  Therefore you must not mount [filename]``/tmp`` with the "
"[option]``noexec`` option."
msgstr ""
"Salt executa ordres remotes des de [filename]./tmp. al sistema de fitxers "
"del client.  Per tant, no heu de muntar [filename]./tmp. amb l'opció [option]"
".noexec.."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "Passing Grains to a Start Event"
msgstr "Passar grains a un esdeveniment inicial"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:68
msgid ""
"Every time a Salt client starts, it passes the ``machine_id`` grain to "
"{productname}. {productname} uses this grain to determine if the client is "
"registered.  This process requires a synchronous Salt call. Synchronous Salt "
"calls block other processes, so if you have a lot of clients start at the "
"same time, the process could create significant delays."
msgstr ""
"Cada vegada que un client de Salt comença, passa el gra  themachineid}. a "
"{productname}. {productname} utilitza aquest gra per determinar si el client "
"està registrat.  Aquest procés requereix una crida síncrona a Salt. Les "
"crides Synchronous Salt bloquegen altres processos, de manera que si tens "
"molts clients comencen al mateix temps, el procés podria crear retards "
"significatius."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:69
msgid ""
"To overcome this problem, a new feature has been introduced in Salt to avoid "
"making a separate synchronous Salt call."
msgstr ""
"Per a superar aquest problema, s'ha introduït una nova característica a Salt "
"per a evitar fer una crida a Salt síncrona separada."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:70
msgid ""
"To use this feature, you can add a configuration parameter to the client "
"configuration, on clients that support it."
msgstr ""
"Per a utilitzar aquesta característica, podeu afegir un paràmetre de "
"configuració a la configuració del client, en els clients que ho suportin."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:71
msgid ""
"To make this process easier, you can use the ``mgr_start_event_grains.sls`` "
"helper Salt state."
msgstr ""
"Per a facilitar aquest procés, podeu utilitzar l'estat de sal de l'ajudant "
"«mgrstarteventgrains.sls»."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:72
msgid ""
"This only applies to already registered clients.  If you registered your "
"Salt client recently, this config parameter is added by default."
msgstr ""
"Això només s'aplica als clients ja registrats.  Si heu registrat el vostre "
"client Salt recentment, aquest paràmetre de configuració s'afegeix per "
"defecte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:73
msgid ""
"On the {productname} Server, at the command prompt, use this command to "
"enable the ``start_event_grains`` configuration helper:"
msgstr ""
"Al servidor {productname}, a l'indicador d'ordres, utilitzeu aquesta ordre "
"per a habilitar l'ajudant de configuració «starteventgrains»:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt '*' state.sls util.mgr_start_event_grains\n"
msgstr "salt '*' state.sls util.mgrstarteventgrains\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:75
msgid ""
"This command adds the required configuration into the client's configuration "
"file, and applies it when the client is restarted.  If you have a large "
"number of clients, you can execute the command in batch mode instead:"
msgstr ""
"Aquesta ordre afegeix la configuració requerida al fitxer de configuració "
"del client, i l'aplica quan es reinicia el client.  Si teniu un gran nombre "
"de clients, podeu executar l'ordre en mode per lots:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt --batch-size 50 '*' state.sls mgr_start_event_grains\n"
msgstr "sal --batch-size 50 '*' estat.sls mgrstarteventgrains\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:77
#, no-wrap
msgid "Proxy Connections and FQDN"
msgstr "Connexions intermediaris i FQDN"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:78
msgid ""
"Sometimes clients connected through a proxy appear in the {webui}, but do "
"not show that they are connected through a proxy.  This can occur if you are "
"not using the fully qualified domain name (FQDN) to connect, and the proxy "
"is not known to {productname}."
msgstr ""
"De vegades els clients connectats a través d'un servidor intermediari "
"apareixen a {webui}, però no mostren que estan connectats a través d'un "
"servidor intermediari.  Això pot passar si no esteu utilitzant el nom de "
"domini completament qualificat (FQDN) per connectar-vos, i el servidor "
"intermediari no és conegut per {productname}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:79
msgid ""
"To correct this behavior, specify additional FQDNs as grains in the client "
"configuration file on the proxy:"
msgstr ""
"Per a corregir aquest comportament, especifiqueu FQDN addicionals com a "
"grans al fitxer de configuració del client al servidor intermediari:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:80
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"grains:\n"
"  susemanager:\n"
"    custom_fqdns:\n"
"      - name.one\n"
"      - name.two\n"
msgstr ""
"grans:\n"
"  gestor de sus:\n"
"    customfqdns:\n"
"      - nom.one\n"
"      - nom.dos\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:81
#, no-wrap
msgid "Red Hat CDN Channel and Multiple Certificates"
msgstr "Canal CDN Red Hat i múltiples certificats"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:82
msgid ""
"The {redhat} content delivery network (CDN) channels sometimes provide "
"multiple certificates, but the {productname} {webui} can only import a "
"single certificate.  If CDN presents a certificate that is different to the "
"one the {productname} {webui} knows about, validation fails and permission "
"to access the repository is denied, even though the certificate is "
"accurate.  The error message received is:"
msgstr ""
"Els canals de {redhat} de la xarxa de lliurament de continguts (CDN) de "
"vegades proporcionen múltiples certificats, però el {productname} {webui} "
"només pot importar un sol certificat.  Si el CDN presenta un certificat "
"diferent del que sap {productname} {webui}, la validació falla i es denega "
"el permís per accedir al repositori, tot i que el certificat és exacte.  El "
"missatge d'error rebut és:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:83
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[error]\n"
"Repository '<repo_name>' is invalid.\n"
"<repo.pem> Valid metadata not found at specified URL\n"
"History:\n"
" - [|] Error trying to read from '<repo.pem>'\n"
" - Permission to access '<repo.pem>' denied.\n"
"Please check if the URIs defined for this repository are pointing to a valid "
"repository.\n"
"Skipping repository '<repo_nam' because of the above error.\n"
"Could not refresh the repositories because of errors.\n"
"HH:MM:SS RepoMDError: Cannot access repository. Maybe repository GPG keys "
"are not imported\n"
msgstr ""
"[error]\n"
"El repositori '<reponame>' no és vàlid.\n"
"<repo.pem> No s'han trobat metadades vàlides a l'URL especificat\n"
"Historial:\n"
" - [ to] Error en intentar llegir des de «<repo.pem>»\n"
" - S'ha denegat el permís per accedir a '<repo.pem>'.\n"
"Comproveu si els URI definits per a aquest repositori apunten a un "
"repositori vàlid.\n"
"S'està ometent el repositori «rereponam» a causa de l'error anterior.\n"
"No s'han pogut actualitzar els repositoris a causa d'errors.\n"
"HH:MM:SS RepoMDError: No es pot accedir al repositori. Potser les claus GPG "
"del repositori no s'importen\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:84
msgid ""
"To resolve this issue, merge all valid certificates into a single ``.pem`` "
"file, and rebuild the certificates for use by {productname}:"
msgstr ""
"Per resoldre aquest problema, fusioneu tots els certificats vàlids en un sol "
"fitxer  the.pem, i reconstruïu els certificats per a usar-los amb "
"{productname}:"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Resolving Multiple {redhat} CDN Certificates"
msgstr "Procediment: Resolució de múltiples {redhat} certificats CDN"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:86
msgid ""
"On the {redhat} client, at the command prompt, as root, gather all current "
"certificates from ``/etc/pki/entitlement/`` in a single ``rh-cert.pem`` "
"file:"
msgstr ""
"Al client {redhat}, a l'indicador d'ordres, com a root, reuneix tots els "
"certificats actuals de  in/etc/pki/entitlement/ in en un sol fitxer  inrh-"
"cert.pem::"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:87
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cat 866705146090697087.pem 3539668047766796506.pem "
"redhat-entitlement-authority.pem > rh-cert.pem\n"
msgstr ""
"cat 866705146090697087.pem 3539668047766796506.pem redhat-entitlement-"
"authority.pem   rh-cert.pem\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:88
msgid ""
"Gather all current keys from ``/etc/pki/entitlement/`` in a single "
"``rh-key.pem`` file:"
msgstr ""
"Recull totes les claus actuals de  in/etc/pki/entitlement/ in en un sol "
"fitxer  inrh-key.pem::"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "cat 866705146090697087-key.pem 3539668047766796506-key.pem > rh-key.pem\n"
msgstr ""
"cat 866705146090697087-key.pem 3539668047766796506-key.pem . rh-key.pem\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:90
msgid ""
"You can now import the new certificates to the {productname} Server, using "
"the instructions in xref:client-configuration:clients-rh-cdn.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Ara podeu importar els certificats nous al servidor {productname}, "
"utilitzant les instruccions a xref:client-configuration:clients-rh-cdn."
"adoc[]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:91
#, no-wrap
msgid "Registration from {webui} fails and does not show any errors"
msgstr "El registre des de {webui} ha fallat i no mostra cap error"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:92
msgid ""
"For the initial registration from the {webui}, all Salt clients are using "
"Salt SSH."
msgstr ""
"Per al registre inicial des de {webui}, tots els clients de Salt estan "
"utilitzant Salt SSH."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:93
msgid ""
"Because of its nature, Salt SSH clients do not report errors back to the "
"server."
msgstr ""
"A causa de la seva naturalesa, els clients de Salt SSH no informen d'errors "
"al servidor."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:94
msgid ""
"However, the Salt SSH clients store a log locally at "
"[path]``/var/log/salt-ssh.log`` that can be inspected for errors."
msgstr ""
"No obstant això, els clients de Salt SSH emmagatzemen un registre local a "
"[path]./var/log/salt-ssh.log. que es pot inspeccionar per errors."

