#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:100
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Rendering SLS 'base:bootstrap' failed: Jinja error: >>> No TLS 1.2 and above "
"for RHEL6 and SLES11. Please check your Apache config.\n"
"...\n"
msgstr ""
"Ha fallat la renderització del SLS «base:bootstrap»: error de Jinja:  T No "
"TLS 1.2 i superior per al RHEL6 i SLES11. Comproveu la configuració de "
"l'Apache.\n"
"...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:101
msgid ""
"This occurs because Apache requires TLS{nbsp}v1.2, but older operating "
"systems do not support this version of the TLS protocol.  To fix this error, "
"you need to force Apache on the server to accept a greater range of protocol "
"versions.  On the {productname} Server, as root, open the "
"[path]``/etc/apache2/ssl-global.conf`` configuration file, locate the "
"[systemitem]``SSLProtocol`` line, and update it to read:"
msgstr ""
"Això passa perquè Apache requereix TLS{nbsp}v1.2, però els sistemes "
"operatius més antics no admeten aquesta versió del protocol TLS.  Per "
"solucionar aquest error, heu de forçar l'Apache al servidor a acceptar un "
"rang més gran de versions de protocol.  Al servidor {productname}, com a "
"root, obriu el fitxer de configuració [path]:/etc/apache2/ssl-global.conf,, "
"localitzeu la línia [systemitem],SSLProtocol, i actualitzeu-la per a llegir:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "SSLProtocol all -SSLv2 -SSLv3\n"
msgstr "SSLProtocol all -SSLv2 -SSLv3\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/tshoot-clients.adoc:103
msgid ""
"This needs to be done manually on the server, and with a Salt state on the "
"Proxy, if applicable.  Restart the [systemitem]``apache`` service on each "
"system after making the changes."
msgstr ""
