msgid ""
"You can use a virtual host manager (VHM) to gather instances from Google "
"Compute Engine (GCE)."
msgstr ""
"Podeu utilitzar un gestor d'amfitrió virtual (VHM) per recollir instàncies "
"de Google Compute Engine (GCE)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-gce.adoc:5
msgid ""
"The VHM you create needs to have the correct permissions assigned to access "
"the GCE VM."
msgstr ""
"La VHM que creeu ha de tenir els permisos correctes assignats per accedir a "
"la VM GCE."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-gce.adoc:6
msgid ""
"Log in to your Google Cloud Platform account as an administrator, and use "
"the Cloud Identity and Access Management (IAM) tool to ensure that the "
"service account has the appropriate roles."
msgstr ""
"Inicieu sessió al vostre compte de Google Cloud Platform com a "
"administrador, i utilitzeu l'eina Cloud Identity and Access Management (IAM) "
"per assegurar que el compte de servei té els rols adequats."

